Você <strong data-start="21" data-end="53">já venceu a parte mais chata</strong>. Agora é só seguir que já já seu site fica NO AR.</p>
<p data-start="105" data-end="218">Estamos aqui 👉 <strong data-start="121" data-end="155">repositório criado com sucesso</strong> ✔️<br data-start="158" data-end="161">
Agora vamos ao próximo passo <strong data-start="190" data-end="217">dentro dessa mesma tela</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="220" data-end="223">
<h2 data-start="225" data-end="281">🧩 PASSO 1 — Criar o <code data-start="249" data-end="261">index.html</code> (o mais importante)</h2>
<h3 data-start="283" data-end="301">1️⃣ Clique em:</h3>
<p data-start="302" data-end="342">👉 <strong data-start="305" data-end="317">Add file</strong><br data-start="317" data-end="320">
👉 <strong data-start="323" data-end="342">Create new file</strong></p>
<h3 data-start="344" data-end="367">2️⃣ Nome do arquivo</h3>
<p data-start="368" data-end="399">Lá em cima, escreve exatamente:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="400" data-end="418"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">diff</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span><span class="hljs-comment">index.html</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="420" data-end="447">3️⃣ Conteúdo do arquivo</h3>
<ul data-start="448" data-end="566">
