w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="113">Calma 😅💙 é mais simples do que parece. Vou te explicar <strong data-start="57" data-end="78">bem passo a passo</strong>, como se eu estivesse do seu lado.</p>
<hr data-start="115" data-end="118">
<h2 data-start="120" data-end="178">🎨 COMO FAZER “ESSE NEGÓCIO DO CANVA” (paleta / visual)</h2>
<h3 data-start="180" data-end="222">📱 OPÇÃO 1 — PELO CELULAR (mais fácil)</h3>
<h3 data-start="224" data-end="246">1️⃣ Entra no Canva</h3>
<p data-start="247" data-end="300">👉 <a data-start="250" data-end="271" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://www.canva.com/">https://www.canva.com<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a><br data-start="271" data-end="274">
ou abre o <strong data-start="284" data-end="300">app do Canva</strong></p>
<p data-start="302" data-end="324">Faz login normalmente.</p>
<hr data-start="326" data-end="329">
<h3 data-start="331" data-end="354">2️⃣ Criar um design</h3>
<ul data-start="355" data-end="454">
<li data-start="355" data-end="384">
<p data-start="357" data-end="384">Toca em <strong data-start="365" data-end="384">Criar um design</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="385" data-end="454">
<p data-start="387" data-end="454">Escolhe <strong data-start="395" data-end="418">Post para Instagram</strong><br data-start="418" data-end="421">
(é o mesmo padrão visual da LAMF)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="456" data-end="459">
<h3 data-start="461" data-end="507">3️⃣ Puxar a paleta da LAMF automaticamente</h3>
<p data-start="508" data-end="539">Isso aqui é o pulo do gato 🐱👇</p>
<h4 data-start="541" data-end="582">🔹 Opção A — Usar uma imagem da LAMF</h4>
<ol data-start="583" data-end="792">
<li data-start="583" data-end="605">
<p data-start="586" data-end="605">Toca em <strong data-start="594" data-end="605">Uploads</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="606" data-end="669">
<p data-start="609" data-end="669">Sobe <strong data-start="614" data-end="654">uma imagem do Instagram @lamf.unifaa</strong> (logo ou post)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="670" data-end="698">
<p data-start="673" data-end="698">Coloca a imagem no design</p>
</li>
<li data-start="699" data-end="716">
<p data-start="702" data-end="716">Toca na imagem</p>
</li>
<li data-start="717" data-end="736">
<p data-start="720" data-end="736">Vai em <strong data-start="727" data-end="736">Cores</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="737" data-end="792">
<p data-start="740" data-end="792">O Canva vai mostrar as <strong data-start="763" data-end="792">cores extraídas da imagem</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="794" data-end="835">👉 Essas são as cores “oficiais” da liga.</p>
<hr data-start="837" data-end="840">
<h4 data-start="842" data-end="891">🔹 Opção B — Escolher manual (mais controle)</h4>
<p data-start="892" data-end="901">No Canva:</p>
<ol data-start="902" data-end="1067">
<li data-start="902" data-end="931">
<p data-start="905" data-end="931">Clica em qualquer elemento</p>
</li>
<li data-start="932" data-end="949">
<p data-start="935" data-end="949">Vai em <strong data-start="942" data-end="949">Cor</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="950" data-end="1067">
<p data-start="953" data-end="976">Usa tons parecidos com:</p>
<ul data-start="980" data-end="1067">
<li data-start="980" data-end="997">
<p data-start="982" data-end="997">Verde escuro 🌿</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1001" data-end="1017">
<p data-start="1003" data-end="1017">Verde claro 🌱</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1021" data-end="1042">
<p data-start="1023" data-end="1042">Bege / off-white 🤍</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1046" data-end="1067">
<p data-start="1048" data-end="1067">Preto ou grafite 🖤</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1069" data-end="1138">Se quiser, posso <strong data-start="1086" data-end="1119">te dizer os códigos certinhos</strong> pra você só colar.</p>
<hr data-start="1140" data-end="1143">
<h3 data-start="1145" data-end="1189">4️⃣ Deixar com cara de Instagram da liga</h3>
<p data-start="1190" data-end="1201">Usa sempre:</p>
<ul data-start="1202" data-end="1322">
<li data-start="1202" data-end="1252">
<p data-start="1204" data-end="1252">Fonte simples (Montserrat, Poppins ou Open Sans)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1253" data-end="1286">
<p data-start="1255" data-end="1286">Poucas cores (2 ou 3 no máximo)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1287" data-end="1300">
<p data-start="1289" data-end="1300">Fundo claro</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1301" data-end="1322">
<p data-start="1303" data-end="1322">Ícones minimalistas</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1324" data-end="1341">📌 Pensa assim:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1342" data-end="1379">
<p data-start="1344" data-end="1379">“Post que eu veria no feed da LAMF”</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="1381" data-end="1384">
<h2 data-start="1386" data-end="1436">🖥️ OPÇÃO 2 — NO COMPUTADOR (se estiver usando)</h2>
<p data-start="1438" data-end="1451">É igualzinho:</p>
<ul data-start="1452" data-end="1530">
<li data-start="1452" data-end="1466">
<p data-start="1454" data-end="1466">Criar design</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1467" data-end="1483">
<p data-start="1469" data-end="1483">Post Instagram</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1484" data-end="1502">
<p data-start="1486" data-end="1502">Upload da imagem</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1503" data-end="1530">
<p data-start="1505" data-end="1530">Cores → paleta automática</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1532" data-end="1535">
<h2 data-start="1537" data-end="1573">❓ PRA QUE ISSO SERVE NO SEU SITE?</h2>
<p data-start="1574" data-end="1588">Você vai usar:</p>
<ul data-start="1589" data-end="1678">
<li data-start="1589" data-end="1610">
<p data-start="1591" data-end="1610"><strong data-start="1591" data-end="1610">As mesmas cores</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1611" data-end="1678">
<p data-start="1613" data-end="1678"><strong data-start="1613" data-end="1630">A mesma fonte</strong><br>
no site → fica tudo profissional e padronizado.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1680" data-end="1683">
<h3 data-start="1685" data-end="1702">Agora me diz:</h3>
<p data-start="1703" data-end="1850" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">👉 você já tem <strong data-start="1718" data-end="1740">uma imagem da LAMF</strong> salva aí pra subir no Canva<br data-start="1768" data-end="1771">
