Você <strong data-start="21" data-end="52">já fez a parte mais difícil</strong>. Tá tudo certo nessa tela.</p>
<p data-start="81" data-end="140">Agora é só <strong data-start="92" data-end="128">FINALIZAR e colocar o site no ar</strong>. Faz assim:</p>
<hr data-start="142" data-end="145">
<h2 data-start="147" data-end="178">✅ PASSO 1 — Salvar o arquivo</h2>
<p data-start="179" data-end="209">No canto <strong data-start="188" data-end="208">superior direito</strong>:</p>
<p data-start="211" data-end="240">👉 Clica no botão <strong data-start="229" data-end="238">verde</strong></p>
<h3 data-start="241" data-end="264"><strong data-start="245" data-end="264">Commit changes…</strong></h3>
<p data-start="266" data-end="289">Vai abrir um quadrinho:</p>
<ul data-start="291" data-end="392">
<li data-start="291" data-end="354">
<p data-start="293" data-end="354">Deixa a mensagem como está (ou escreve: <code data-start="333" data-end="353">Criando index.html</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="355" data-end="392">
<p data-start="357" data-end="392">Clica em <strong data-start="366" data-end="384">Commit changes</strong> de novo</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="394" data-end="425">✔️ Pronto, o arquivo foi salvo.</p>
<hr data-start="427" data-end="430">
<h2 data-start="432" data-end="476">🌐 PASSO 2 — Ativar o site (GitHub Pages)</h2>
<p data-start="478" data-end="499">Agora olha com calma:</p>
<p data-start="501" data-end="623">1️⃣ Volta para a página principal do repositório<br data-start="549" data-end="552">
2️⃣ Clica em <strong data-start="565" data-end="577">Settings</strong><br data-start="577" data-end="580">
3️⃣ No menu da esquerda, clica em <strong data-start="614" data-end="623">Pages</strong></p>
<hr data-start="625" data-end="628">
<h3 data-start="630" data-end="650">Dentro de Pages:</h3>
<ul data-start="651" data-end="790">
<li data-start="651" data-end="713">
<p data-start="653" data-end="678">Em <strong data-start="656" data-end="666">Source</strong>, seleciona:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="681" data-end="713"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">css</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>Deploy </span><span><span class="hljs-selector-tag">from</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-selector-tag">a</span></span><span> branch
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
</li>
<li data-start="714" data-end="758">
<p data-start="716" data-end="739">Em <strong data-start="719" data-end="729">Branch</strong>, escolhe:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="742" data-end="758"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">css</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span><span class="hljs-selector-tag">main</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
</li>
<li data-start="759" data-end="790">
<p data-start="761" data-end="767">Pasta:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="770" data-end="790"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1"></div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>/ (root)
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="792" data-end="812">👉 Clica em <strong data-start="804" data-end="812">Save</strong></p>
<hr data-start="814" data-end="817">
<h2 data-start="819" data-end="855">🔗 PASSO 3 — Pegar o link do site</h2>
<p data-start="856" data-end="905">Depois de alguns segundos (às vezes 1 minutinho):</p>
<p data-start="907" data-end="938">O GitHub vai mostrar algo como:</p>
