first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="168">AAAAA 😍🎉 <strong data-start="11" data-end="20">BOA!!</strong><br data-start="20" data-end="23">
Parabéns, Leandra — <strong data-start="43" data-end="79">seu site está oficialmente no ar</strong> 🐱💚<br data-start="84" data-end="87">
Isso é coisa de gente grande, viu? Liga acadêmica com site próprio = outro nível.</p>
<p data-start="170" data-end="246">Agora vamos deixar ele <strong data-start="193" data-end="243">com a cara da LAMF no Instagram (@lamf.unifaa)</strong> 👇</p>
<hr data-start="248" data-end="251">
<h2 data-start="253" data-end="301">🎨 PRÓXIMO PASSO — Visual “Instagram da Liga”</h2>
<h3 data-start="303" data-end="360">Paleta que combina com a LAMF (sugestão profissional)</h3>
<p data-start="361" data-end="390">A gente pode usar algo assim:</p>
<ul data-start="391" data-end="508">
<li data-start="391" data-end="421">
<p data-start="393" data-end="421">💙 Azul principal: <code data-start="412" data-end="421">#1f3c88</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="422" data-end="448">
<p data-start="424" data-end="448">🩵 Azul claro: <code data-start="439" data-end="448">#4a6fa5</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="449" data-end="471">
<p data-start="451" data-end="471">🤍 Branco: <code data-start="462" data-end="471">#ffffff</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="472" data-end="508">
<p data-start="474" data-end="508">🖤 Cinza escuro (texto): <code data-start="499" data-end="508">#2e2e2e</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="510" data-end="551">Se quiser, dá pra ajustar depois fininho.</p>
<hr data-start="553" data-end="556">
<h2 data-start="558" data-end="578">🖼️ Logo do Canva</h2>
<p data-start="579" data-end="648">Você comentou do <strong data-start="596" data-end="605">Canva</strong>, então vamos usar ele do jeito mais fácil:</p>
<h3 data-start="650" data-end="665">Como fazer:</h3>
<p data-start="666" data-end="818">1️⃣ Abre o <strong data-start="677" data-end="686">Canva</strong><br>
2️⃣ Cria um design → <strong data-start="708" data-end="716">Logo</strong> ou <strong data-start="720" data-end="738">Post Instagram</strong><br>
3️⃣ Usa as cores da LAMF<br data-start="763" data-end="766">
4️⃣ Baixa como <strong data-start="781" data-end="788">PNG</strong> (fundo transparente se tiver)</p>
<p data-start="820" data-end="832">Depois você:</p>
<ul data-start="833" data-end="929">
<li data-start="833" data-end="852">
<p data-start="835" data-end="852">Volta no GitHub</p>
</li>
<li data-start="853" data-end="891">
<p data-start="855" data-end="891">Clica em <strong data-start="864" data-end="891">Add file → Upload files</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="892" data-end="929">
<p data-start="894" data-end="929">Sobe a imagem (ex: <code data-start="913" data-end="928">logo-lamf.png</code>)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="931" data-end="988">Eu já te digo <strong data-start="945" data-end="970">onde encaixar no site</strong>, sem complicação.</p>
<hr data-start="990" data-end="993">
<h2 data-start="995" data-end="1027">🔘 Botões úteis (fica chique)</h2>
<p data-start="1028" data-end="1049">A gente pode colocar:</p>
<ul data-start="1050" data-end="1122">
<li data-start="1050" data-end="1071">
<p data-start="1052" data-end="1071">Instagram da Liga</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1072" data-end="1097">
<p data-start="1074" data-end="1097">Linktree Cat Friendly</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1098" data-end="1110">
<p data-start="1100" data-end="1110">Projetos</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1111" data-end="1122">
<p data-start="1113" data-end="1122">Contato</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1124" data-end="1166">Tudo com botão bonitinho, mobile-friendly.</p>
<hr data-start="1168" data-end="1171">
<p data-start="1173" data-end="1286">Agora me diz:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="1190" data-end="1286">Você já tem a logo da LAMF pronta no Canva ou quer que eu te diga exatamente como montar lá?</strong></p>
<p data-start="1288" data-end="1373" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">A partir disso, deixo esse site com cara de <strong data-start="1332" data-end="1368">projeto institucional de verdade</strong> 💚🐾</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copiar" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resposta satisfatória" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover