alse" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Editar mensagem" aria-pressed="false" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="5e2960cf-3003-457f-9984-6433a56cde46" data-testid="conversation-turn-40" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only">O ChatGPT disse:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="c7c143d5-073b-4df8-affa-ca9da3e3b388" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="181">Claro — e sim, a gente <strong data-start="23" data-end="110">vai pegar TODO o conteúdo que você já colocou no seu Linktree e colocar no seu site</strong> de forma organizada, com seções e botões bonitos igual no Instagram 👇</p>
<p data-start="183" data-end="453">⚠️ <strong data-start="186" data-end="256">Só não consigo puxar o conteúdo automaticamente da página Linktree</strong>, porque ela carrega os links dinamicamente e não mostra o texto completo para mim diretamente.<br data-start="351" data-end="354">
Mas você me ajudou mostrando que o Linktree existe — agora eu preciso <strong data-start="424" data-end="450">do que tinha lá dentro</strong> 💡</p>
<p data-start="455" data-end="629">📌 Por exemplo, no seu Linktree provavelmente tem:<br>
✔️ Instagram da LAMF<br data-start="526" data-end="529">
✔️ Cartilha CatFriendly<br data-start="552" data-end="555">
✔️ Guias, artigos e PDFs<br data-start="579" data-end="582">
✔️ Vídeos<br data-start="591" data-end="594">
✔️ Contatos<br data-start="605" data-end="608">
✔️ Outros links úteis</p>
<p data-start="631" data-end="742">👉 <strong data-start="634" data-end="717">Me conta aqui: quais são todos os links / títulos que aparecem no seu Linktree?</strong><br data-start="717" data-end="720">
Você pode fazer assim:</p>
<p data-start="744" data-end="860">➡️ Abrir o Linktree (<a data-start="765" data-end="794" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://linktr.ee/Catfriendly?utm_source=chatgpt.com">https://linktr.ee/Catfriendly<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a>)<br data-start="795" data-end="798">
➡️ Copiar os nomes dos botões e qualquer texto<br data-start="844" data-end="847">
➡️ Colar aqui</p>
<p data-start="862" data-end="896">Por exemplo, pode responder assim:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="898" data-end="1043"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">mathematica</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>📍 </span><span><span class="hljs-variable">Cartilha</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-variable">CatFriendly</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-operator">-</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">PDF</span></span><span>
📍 </span><span><span class="hljs-variable">Instagram</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-variable">dos</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-variable">Profissionais</span></span><span>
📍 </span><span><span class="hljs-variable">Artigo</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-variable">Gest</span></span><span>ã</span><span><span class="hljs-variable">o</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-variable">Ambiental</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-variable">Felina</span></span><span>
📍 </span><span><span class="hljs-variable">V</span></span><span>í</span><span><span class="hljs-variable">deos</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-variable">Educativos</span></span><span>
📍 </span><span><span class="hljs-variable">Contato</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-operator">/</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-variable">WhatsApp</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1045" data-end="1182">🔹 Me dá a lista de TODOS os links que tem no seu Linktree.<br data-start="1104" data-end="1107">
🔹 Se tiver descrição embaixo, também manda (tipo um textinho que aparece).</p>
<p data-start="1184" data-end="1255">Quando eu tiver isso, eu vou criar <strong data-start="1219" data-end="1250">uma versão completa do site</strong> com:</p>
<p data-start="1257" data-end="1410">✨ Título bonitão<br data-start="1273" data-end="1276">
✨ Seções claras e navegáveis<br data-start="1304" data-end="1307">
✨ Botões que abrem cada link<br data-start="1335" data-end="1338">
✨ Textos explicativos (se tiver)<br data-start="1370" data-end="1373">
✨ Vídeos embutidos (se tiver YouTube)</p>
<p data-start="1412" data-end="1500">E tudo com o visual <strong data-start="1432" data-end="1479">rosinha harmonizado com o Instagram da LAMF</strong> como combinamos 💗🐱</p>
<p data-start="1502" data-end="1561">👉 Só me mandar a lista dos links e textos do seu Linktree!</p>
