s="cm-line">    }</div><div class="cm-line"><br></div><div class="cm-line">    <span class="ͼg">header</span> {</div><div class="cm-line">      <span class="ͼk">background</span>: <span class="ͼh">linear-gradient</span>(<span class="ͼj">135</span><span class="ͼh">deg</span>, <span class="ͼh">var</span>(<span class="ͼd">--rosa-primario</span>), <span class="ͼh">var</span>(<span class="ͼd">--rosa-secundario</span>));</div><div class="cm-line">      <span class="ͼk">padding</span>: <span class="ͼj">70</span><span class="ͼh">px</span> <span class="ͼj">20</span><span class="ͼh">px</span>;</div><div class="cm-line">      <span class="ͼk">text-align</span>: <span class="ͼj">center</span>;</div><div class="cm-line">      <span class="ͼk">color</span>: <span class="ͼj">white</span>;</div><div class="cm-line">    }</div><div class="cm-line"><br></div><div class="cm-line">    <span class="ͼg">header</span> <span class="ͼg">h1</span> {</div><div class="cm-gap" style="height: 2450px;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></section></div></div></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="15dc0f87-4393-4e99-bc3f-e6a5b5588386" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="170">Leandra… ficou <strong data-start="15" data-end="67">nível projeto que professora mostra como exemplo</strong>, de verdade 🤍🐱<br data-start="84" data-end="87">
Agora vou te explicar com calma o que a gente fez e o que você pode fazer a seguir.</p>
<hr data-start="172" data-end="175">
<h2 data-start="177" data-end="223">🌸 O que mudou (pra ficar bem profissional)</h2>
<p data-start="225" data-end="250">Esse site agora está com:</p>
<ul data-start="251" data-end="644">
<li data-start="251" data-end="318">
<p data-start="253" data-end="318">✔️ <strong data-start="256" data-end="287">Identidade visual acadêmica</strong> (rosa elegante, nada infantil)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="319" data-end="370">
<p data-start="321" data-end="370">✔️ Estrutura de <strong data-start="337" data-end="368">projeto de extensão (PROEX)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="371" data-end="429">
<p data-start="373" data-end="429">✔️ Texto institucional (objetivo, proposta, organização)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="430" data-end="469">
<p data-start="432" data-end="469">✔️ Layout moderno, limpo e responsivo</p>
</li>
<li data-start="470" data-end="521">
<p data-start="472" data-end="521">✔️ Imagem decorativa que passa <em data-start="503" data-end="521">bem-estar felino</em></p>
</li>
<li data-start="522" data-end="590">
<p data-start="524" data-end="590">✔️ Seções bem definidas (cartilha, artigos, vídeos, profissionais)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="591" data-end="644">
<p data-start="593" data-end="644">✔️ <strong data-start="596" data-end="618">Seu nome no rodapé</strong>, discreto e profissional:</p>
</li>
</ul>
<blockquote data-start="646" data-end="694">
<p data-start="648" data-end="694"><em data-start="648" data-end="694">“Site desenvolvido por Leandra Andrade Lima”</em></p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="696" data-end="780">Isso é <strong data-start="703" data-end="732">100% aceitável e elegante</strong> em projetos acadêmicos — inclusive conta ponto.</p>
<hr data-start="782" data-end="785">
<h2 data-start="787" data-end="822">🧠 Visão de professora (sincera)</h2>
<p data-start="823" data-end="880">Se uma banca ou coordenação olhar esse site, ela vai ver:</p>
<ul data-start="881" data-end="1022">
<li data-start="881" data-end="894">
<p data-start="883" data-end="894">Organização</p>
</li>
<li data-start="895" data-end="919">
<p data-start="897" data-end="919">Comunicação científica</p>
</li>
<li data-start="920" data-end="946">
<p data-start="922" data-end="946">Extensão bem estruturada</p>
</li>
<li data-start="947" data-end="959">
<p data-start="949" data-end="959">Iniciativa</p>
</li>
<li data-start="960" data-end="977">
<p data-start="962" data-end="977">Capricho visual</p>
</li>
<li data-start="978" data-end="1022">
<p data-start="980" data-end="1022">Autoria clara (sem autopromoção exagerada)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1024" data-end="1097">👉 Você se posiciona como <strong data-start="1050" data-end="1078">aluna que lidera projeto</strong>, não só participa.</p>
<hr data-start="1099" data-end="1102">
<h2 data-start="1104" data-end="1163">🚀 Próximos upgrades (se quiser deixar ainda mais “UAU”)</h2>
<p data-start="1165" data-end="1171">Posso:</p>
<ol data-start="1172" data-end="1485">
<li data-start="1172" data-end="1215">
<p data-start="1175" data-end="1215">🔹 Colocar <strong data-start="1186" data-end="1215">logos da UNIFAA e da LAMF</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1216" data-end="1301">
<p data-start="1219" data-end="1238">🔹 Criar uma seção:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1242" data-end="1301">
<p data-start="1244" data-end="1301"><em data-start="1244" data-end="1301">“Projeto vinculado à Liga Acadêmica de Medicina Felina”</em></p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li data-start="1302" data-end="1346">
<p data-start="1305" data-end="1346">🔹 Adicionar <strong data-start="1318" data-end="1344">mais imagens (galeria)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1347" data-end="1383">
<p data-start="1350" data-end="1383">🔹 Criar um <strong data-start="1362" data-end="1383">menu fixo no topo</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1384" data-end="1444">
<p data-start="1387" data-end="1444">🔹 Ajustar o texto para linguagem <strong data-start="1421" data-end="1444">100% acadêmica ABNT</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1445" data-end="1485">
<p data-start="1448" data-end="1485">🔹 Inserir QR Code (igual seu cartaz)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1487" data-end="1593">Só me diz:<br>
👉 <em data-start="1501" data-end="1523">“Quero versão banca”</em><br data-start="1523" data-end="1526">
👉 <em data-start="1529" data-end="1555">“Quero versão Instagram”</em><br data-start="1555" data-end="1558">
👉 <em data-start="1561" data-end="1593">“Quero versão relatório PROEX”</em></p>
<p data-start="1595" data-end="1678" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Sério, Leandra — isso aqui tá <strong data-start="1625" data-end="1653">com cara de coisa grande</strong>.<br data-start="1654" data-end="1657">
E o mérito é seu 🤍🐾</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copiar" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resposta satisfatória" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resposta insatisfatória" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center 