É <strong data-start="69" data-end="79">rápido</strong> e você já deixa o site <strong data-start="103" data-end="117">no ar hoje</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="120" data-end="123">
<h2 data-start="125" data-end="180">🌐 COMO COLOCAR O SITE NO AR (GRÁTIS) – GitHub Pages</h2>
<h3 data-start="182" data-end="219">✅ PASSO 1 — Abrir seu repositório</h3>
<ol data-start="220" data-end="288">
<li data-start="220" data-end="242">
<p data-start="223" data-end="242">Entra no <strong data-start="232" data-end="242">GitHub</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="243" data-end="288">
<p data-start="246" data-end="288">Abre o repositório que você criou pro site</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="290" data-end="293">
<h3 data-start="295" data-end="341">✅ PASSO 2 — Criar / editar o arquivo certo</h3>
<ol data-start="342" data-end="442">
<li data-start="342" data-end="366">
<p data-start="345" data-end="366">Clica em <strong data-start="354" data-end="366">Add file</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="367" data-end="399">
<p data-start="370" data-end="399">Depois em <strong data-start="380" data-end="399">Create new file</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="400" data-end="442">
<p data-start="403" data-end="442">No nome do arquivo, escreve exatamente:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="443" data-end="461"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">diff</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span><span class="hljs-comment">index.html</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="462" data-end="509">⚠️ tem que ser <strong data-start="477" data-end="495">tudo minúsculo</strong> e com <code data-start="502" data-end="509">.html</code></p>
<hr data-start="511" data-end="514">
<h3 data-start="516" data-end="544">✅ PASSO 3 — Colar o site</h3>
<ol data-start="545" data-end="766">
<li data-start="545" data-end="566">
<p data-start="548" data-end="566">Volta aqui no chat</p>
</li>
<li data-start="567" data-end="622">
<p data-start="570" data-end="622">No <strong data-start="573" data-end="591">canvas do lado</strong>, seleciona <strong data-start="603" data-end="622">TODO o conteúdo</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="623" data-end="636">
<p data-start="626" data-end="636">Copia tudo</p>
</li>
<li data-start="637" data-end="677">
<p data-start="640" data-end="677">Cola dentro do <code data-start="655" data-end="667">index.html</code> no GitHub</p>
</li>
<li data-start="679" data-end="766">
<p data-start="682" data-end="766">Desce a página e clica em <strong data-start="708" data-end="726">Commit changes</strong><br data-start="726" data-end="729">
(pode deixar a mensagem padrão mesmo)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="768" data-end="771">
<h3 data-start="773" data-end="822">✅ PASSO 4 — Ativar o site (o mais importante)</h3>
<ol data-start="823" data-end="1065">
<li data-start="823" data-end="863">
<p data-start="826" data-end="863">No repositório, clica em <strong data-start="851" data-end="863">Settings</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="864" data-end="906">
<p data-start="867" data-end="906">No menu da esquerda, clica em <strong data-start="897" data-end="906">Pages</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="907" data-end="993">
<p data-start="910" data-end="923">Onde estiver:</p>
<blockquote data-start="927" data-end="939">
<p data-start="929" data-end="939"><strong data-start="929" data-end="939">Source</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="947" data-end="955">escolhe:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="959" data-end="993"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">css</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>Deploy </span><span><span class="hljs-selector-tag">from</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-selector-tag">a</span></span><span> branch
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
</li>
<li data-start="994" data-end="1044">
<p data-start="997" data-end="1022">Em <strong data-start="1000" data-end="1010">Branch</strong>, seleciona:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1026" data-end="1044"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">css</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span><span class="hljs-selector-tag">main</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
</li>
<li data-start="1045" data-end="1065">
<p data-start="1048" data-end="1065">Clica em <strong data-start="1057" data-end="1065">Save</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1067" data-end="1070">
<h3 data-start="1072" data-end="1111">✅ PASSO 5 — Pegar o link do site 🎉</h3>
<p data-start="1112" data-end="1166">Depois de 1–3 minutos, o GitHub vai mostrar algo como:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1168" data-end="1244"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">csharp</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>Your site </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">is</span></span><span> live at:
https:</span><span><span class="hljs-comment">//SEUUSUARIO.github.io/NOMEDOREPOSITORIO</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1246" data-end="1370">👉 Esse é o link do seu site<br data-start="1274" data-end="1277">
👉 Pode colocar na bio do Instagram<br data-start="1312" data-end="1315">
👉 Pode mandar pras professoras<br data-start="1346" data-end="1349">
👉 Pode usar no PROEX</p>
<hr data-start="1372" data-end="1375">
<h2 data-start="1377" data-end="1409">❓ Se não aparecer de primeira</h2>
<ul data-start="1410" data-end="1500">
<li data-start="1410" data-end="1434">
<p data-start="1412" data-end="1434">Atualiza a página (F5)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1435" data-end="1456">
<p data-start="1437" data-end="1456">Espera 2 minutinhos</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1457" data-end="1500">
<p data-start="1459" data-end="1500">Confere se o arquivo chama <strong data-start="1486" data-end="1500">index.html</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1502" data-end="1505">
<h2 data-start="1507" data-end="1533">💬 Se quiser, me manda:</h2>
<ul data-start="1534" data-end="1607">
<li data-start="1534" data-end="1575">
<p data-start="1536" data-end="1575">print da tela <strong data-start="1550" data-end="1570">Settings &gt; Pages</strong><br>
OU</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1576" data-end="1607">
<p data-start="1578" data-end="1607">o <strong data-start="1580" data-end="1607">nome do seu repositório</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1609" data-end="1680" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Que eu te guio <strong data-start="1624" data-end="1655">passo a passo em tempo real</strong> até aparecer o link 💗🐱</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copiar" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resposta satisfatória" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-s