<h2 data-start="754" data-end="795">📌 2) <strong data-start="763" data-end="795">Freelance Portfolio Template</strong></h2>
<p data-start="796" data-end="913">👉 Um template de portfólio moderno com <strong data-start="836" data-end="861">HTML, CSS e Bootstrap</strong>, pronto para personalizar.<br data-start="888" data-end="891">
