<p data-start="1021" data-end="1131">🔗 Repositório: <strong data-start="1037" data-end="1093">Iamdivyak/Freelance-Web-Developer-Portfolio-Template</strong> <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 45px;"><a href="https://github.com/Iamdivyak/Freelance-Web-Developer-Portfolio-Template?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://github.com/Iamdivyak/Freelance-Web-Developer-Portfolio-Template?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]!" style="max-width: 45px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">GitHub</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
