<p data-start="1175" data-end="1360">👉 Template mais moderno com efeitos visuais (transparências, cartões visuais estilo <em data-start="1260" data-end="1267">glass</em>) e seção de projetos detalhados.<br data-start="1300" data-end="1303">
Esse é ótimo se você quer um visual <strong data-start="1339" data-end="1359">mais tech/design</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1362" data-end="1450">🔗 Repositório: <strong data-start="1378" data-end="1412">MrPrince419/portfolio-template</strong> <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 45px;"><a href="https://github.com/MrPrince419/portfolio-template?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://github.com/MrPrince419/portfolio-template?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]!" style="max-width: 45px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">GitHub</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<hr data-start="1452" data-end="1455">
<h2 data-start="1457" data-end="1496">✨ Como usar um desses no seu projeto</h2>
<h3 data-start="1498" data-end="1527">✅ Passo 1 — Fork (copiar)</h3>
<ol data-start="1528" data-end="1677">
<li data-start="1528" data-end="1591">
<p data-start="1531" data-end="1591">Acesse o repositório escolhido (ex: o <em data-start="1569" data-end="1589">portfolio_one-page</em>).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1592" data-end="1639">
<p data-start="1595" data-end="1639">Clique em <strong data-start="1605" data-end="1613">Fork</strong> (canto superior direito).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1640" data-end="1677">
<p data-start="1643" data-end="1677">Isso cria uma cópia no seu GitHub.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1679" data-end="1682">
<h3 data-start="1684" data-end="1733">✅ Passo 2 — Baixar ou editar direto no GitHub</h3>
