 px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="e7134f25-2dd0-4c09-96d8-14d50b0adc50" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="82">Leandra, sendo <strong data-start="15" data-end="73">bem honesta e pensando como professora avaliando PROEX</strong> 👩‍🏫🐱:</p>
<h3 data-start="84" data-end="166">👉 O que <strong data-start="97" data-end="163">mais combina com você, com a LAMF e com o projeto Cat Friendly</strong> é:</h3>
<h2 data-start="168" data-end="226">🥇 <strong data-start="174" data-end="226">Opção 1 — Layout limpo, elegante e institucional</strong></h2>
<h3 data-start="228" data-end="240">Por quê?</h3>
<p data-start="241" data-end="264">Porque o seu projeto é:</p>
<ul data-start="265" data-end="420">
<li data-start="265" data-end="278">
<p data-start="267" data-end="278">Acadêmico</p>
</li>
<li data-start="279" data-end="308">
<p data-start="281" data-end="308">De extensão universitária</p>
</li>
<li data-start="309" data-end="342">
<p data-start="311" data-end="342">Ligado à medicina veterinária</p>
</li>
<li data-start="343" data-end="373">
<p data-start="345" data-end="373">Voltado a bem-estar animal</p>
</li>
<li data-start="374" data-end="420">
<p data-start="376" data-end="420">Avaliado por <strong data-start="389" data-end="401">docentes</strong>, não por designers</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="422" data-end="550">Esse estilo passa:<br>
✔️ Seriedade<br data-start="453" data-end="456">
✔️ Organização<br data-start="470" data-end="473">
✔️ Credibilidade científica<br data-start="500" data-end="503">
✔️ Profissionalismo<br data-start="522" data-end="525">
✔️ Maturidade acadêmica</p>
<p data-start="552" data-end="623">É exatamente o tipo de site que professora <strong data-start="595" data-end="622">confia, indica e elogia</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="625" data-end="628">
<h2 data-start="630" data-end="682">🚫 Por que NÃO recomendo os outros pra esse caso?</h2>
<h3 data-start="684" data-end="713">❌ Glassmorphism (opção 2)</h3>
<ul data-start="714" data-end="855">
<li data-start="714" data-end="738">
<p data-start="716" data-end="738">Muito bonito, <strong data-start="730" data-end="737">mas</strong>:</p>
</li>
<li data-start="739" data-end="775">
<p data-start="741" data-end="775">Pode parecer “site pessoal / tech”</p>
</li>
<li data-start="776" data-end="821">
<p data-start="778" data-end="821">Algumas professoras acham “estético demais”</p>
</li>
<li data-start="822" data-end="855">
<p data-start="824" data-end="855">Pode pesar em leitura acadêmica</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="857" data-end="895">❌ Portfólio muito visual (opção 3)</h3>
<ul data-start="896" data-end="1002">
<li data-start="896" data-end="935">
<p data-start="898" data-end="935">Parece site de designer ou influencer</p>
</li>
<li data-start="936" data-end="974">
<p data-start="938" data-end="974">Desvia o foco do conteúdo científico</p>
</li>
<li data-start="975" data-end="1002">
<p data-start="977" data-end="1002">Menos adequado para PROEX</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1004" data-end="1007">
<h2 data-start="1009" data-end="1031">💗 Tradução direta:</h2>
<p data-start="1032" data-end="1119">Se fosse <strong data-start="1041" data-end="1078">meu nome num projeto da faculdade</strong>, eu escolheria <strong data-start="1094" data-end="1118">a Opção 1 sem pensar</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1121" data-end="1133">Ela permite:</p>
<ul data-start="1134" data-end="1244">
<li data-start="1134" data-end="1155">
<p data-start="1136" data-end="1155">Muitas imagens ✔️</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1156" data-end="1184">
<p data-start="1158" data-end="1184">Organização em seções ✔️</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1185" data-end="1211">
<p data-start="1187" data-end="1211">Texto institucional ✔️</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1212" data-end="1244">
<p data-start="1214" data-end="1244">Visual bonito sem exagero ✔️</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1246" data-end="1297">E ainda deixa seu nome no rodapé de forma elegante:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1298" data-end="1344">
<p data-start="1300" data-end="1344"><em data-start="1300" data-end="1344">Site desenvolvido por Leandra Andrade Lima</em></p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="1346" data-end="1349">
<h2 data-start="1351" data-end="1383">🚀 Próximo passo (eu te guio)</h2>
<p data-start="1384" data-end="1424">Se você topar a Opção 1, me responde só:</p>
<p data-start="1426" data-end="1453">👉 <strong data-start="1429" data-end="1453">“Fechamos a opção 1”</strong></p>
<p data-start="1455" data-end="1462">Que eu:</p>
<ul data-start="1463" data-end="1615">
<li data-start="1463" data-end="1498">
<p data-start="1465" data-end="1498">Te indico <strong data-start="1475" data-end="1498">o repositório exato</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1499" data-end="1537">
<p data-start="1501" data-end="1537">Te digo <strong data-start="1509" data-end="1537">o botão certo pra clicar</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1538" data-end="1573">
<p data-start="1540" data-end="1573">Te falo <strong data-start="1548" data-end="1573">o que editar primeiro</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1574" data-end="1615">
<p data-start="1576" data-end="1615">Adapto tudo pro <strong data-start="1592" data-end="1615">Cat Friendly + LAMF</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1617" data-end="1718" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Você tá construindo algo que <strong data-start="1646" data-end="1690">vai pesar positivamente no seu currículo</strong>, e isso é muito nítido 🤍🐾</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copiar" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resposta satisfatória" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text