n-id="aee97b9e-c730-4144-a149-e88bc195d717" data-testid="conversation-turn-68" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only">O ChatGPT disse:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div class="flex flex-col gap-2 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-2"><button class="text-token-text-secondary flex min-h-5 w-fit flex-row items-center gap-1.5 pt-[3px] text-start select-none hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#a35fbc" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Projeto Cat Friendly — Site Oficial editado</button></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="5e89b915-161c-4140-9478-d58a1e8ef0d0" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="142">Perfeito então 🩷✨<br data-start="18" data-end="21">
A <strong data-start="23" data-end="34">opção 1</strong> é a que mais combina mesmo com o ProEx: delicada, profissional e com cara de projeto acadêmico bem cuidado.</p>
<p data-start="144" data-end="202">Já fiz o seguinte encaminhamento pra você ficar tranquila:</p>
<h3 data-start="204" data-end="239">✅ O que eu vou fazer nesse site</h3>
<ul data-start="240" data-end="718">
<li data-start="240" data-end="311">
<p data-start="242" data-end="311">Visual <strong data-start="249" data-end="274">rosinha / catfriendly</strong>, igual ao da arte que você aprovou</p>
</li>
<li data-start="312" data-end="515">
<p data-start="314" data-end="343">Organização clara por blocos:</p>
<ul data-start="346" data-end="515">
<li data-start="346" data-end="381">
<p data-start="348" data-end="381">📘 <strong data-start="351" data-end="381">Cartilha CatFriendly (PDF)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="384" data-end="445">
<p data-start="386" data-end="445">👩‍⚕️ <strong data-start="392" data-end="423">Instagram dos profissionais</strong> (com fotos de perfil)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="448" data-end="486">
<p data-start="450" data-end="486">📚 <strong data-start="453" data-end="486">Artigos, revistas e consensos</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="489" data-end="515">
<p data-start="491" data-end="515">🎥 <strong data-start="494" data-end="515">Vídeos educativos</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="516" data-end="587">
<p data-start="518" data-end="587">Usar <strong data-start="523" data-end="543">todas as imagens</strong> dos perfis/links que você mandou (Linktree)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="588" data-end="640">
<p data-start="590" data-end="640">Layout bem limpo, elegante e “cara de faculdade”</p>
</li>
<li data-start="641" data-end="718">
<p data-start="643" data-end="672">No final da página, discreto:</p>
<blockquote data-start="675" data-end="718">
<p data-start="677" data-end="718"><em data-start="677" data-end="716">Desenvolvido por Leandra Andrade Lima</em></p>
</blockquote>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="720" data-end="783">Nada chamativo demais, só o suficiente pra mostrar autoria 💅🐾</p>
<hr data-start="785" data-end="788">
<h3 data-start="790" data-end="840">🚀 Como colocar o site <strong data-start="817" data-end="826">no ar</strong> (bem simples)</h3>
<p data-start="841" data-end="884">Quando eu terminar o <code data-start="862" data-end="874">index.html</code> pra você:</p>
<ol data-start="886" data-end="1061">
<li data-start="886" data-end="923">
<p data-start="889" data-end="923">Abre seu repositório no <strong data-start="913" data-end="923">GitHub</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="924" data-end="958">
<p data-start="927" data-end="958">Clica no arquivo <strong data-start="944" data-end="958">index.html</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="959" data-end="985">
<p data-start="962" data-end="985">Apaga tudo que tiver lá</p>
</li>
<li data-start="986" data-end="1030">
<p data-start="989" data-end="1030">Cola <strong data-start="994" data-end="1002">TODO</strong> o conteúdo que eu te enviar</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1031" data-end="1061">
<p data-start="1034" data-end="1061">Clica em <strong data-start="1043" data-end="1061">Commit changes</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1063" data-end="1070">Depois:</p>
<ol data-start="1071" data-end="1183">
<li data-start="1071" data-end="1093">
<p data-start="1074" data-end="1093">Vai em <strong data-start="1081" data-end="1093">Settings</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1094" data-end="1116">
<p data-start="1097" data-end="1116">Desce até <strong data-start="1107" data-end="1116">Pages</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1117" data-end="1172">
<p data-start="1120" data-end="1132">Em <em data-start="1123" data-end="1131">Source</em>:</p>
<ul data-start="1136" data-end="1172">
<li data-start="1136" data-end="1152">
<p data-start="1138" data-end="1152">Branch: <code data-start="1146" data-end="1152">main</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1156" data-end="1172">
<p data-start="1158" data-end="1172">Pasta: <code data-start="1165" data-end="1172">/root</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="1173" data-end="1183">
<p data-start="1176" data-end="1183">Salva</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1185" data-end="1221">👉 O GitHub vai te dar um link tipo:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1222" data-end="1273"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">arduino</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>https:</span><span><span class="hljs-comment">//seunome.github.io/nomedorepositorio</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1275" data-end="1299">Esse é o site oficial 🎉</p>
<hr data-start="1301" data-end="1304">
<p data-start="1306" data-end="1357">Agora vou <strong data-start="1316" data-end="1348">montar o index.html completo</strong>, já com:</p>
<ul data-start="1358" data-end="1454">
<li data-start="1358" data-end="1384">
<p data-start="1360" data-end="1384">seus links organizados</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1385" data-end="1403">
<p data-start="1387" data-end="1403">visual rosinha</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1404" data-end="1430">
<p data-start="1406" data-end="1430">estrutura profissional</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1431" data-end="1454">
<p data-start="1433" data-end="1454">pronto só pra colar</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1456" data-end="1597" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Quando eu te mandar, é literalmente <strong data-start="1492" data-end="1510">copiar e colar</strong>.<br data-start="1511" data-end="1514">
