ndly — Site Oficial</button><button class="text-token-text-secondary flex min-h-5 w-fit flex-row items-center gap-1.5 pt-[3px] text-start select-none hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#a35fbc" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>7 edições realizadas em Projeto Cat Friendly — Site Oficial</button></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="c31ba73a-49cd-4791-bc5e-6b58a1a35944" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2-thinking"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="32">Fechado — já ajustei o site pra:</p>
<ul data-start="34" data-end="319">
<li data-start="34" data-end="92">
<p data-start="36" data-end="92"><strong data-start="36" data-end="88">Cartilha abrir o SEU PDF (local no GitHub Pages)</strong> ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-start="93" data-end="182">
<p data-start="95" data-end="182"><strong data-start="95" data-end="140">Imagem da capa da cartilha ficar clicável</strong> (a pessoa clica na capa e abre o PDF) ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-start="183" data-end="319">
<p data-start="185" data-end="319"><strong data-start="185" data-end="215">Profissionais com Nome + @</strong> (deixei 2 completos e 4 como “preencher”, porque esses 4 links <code data-start="279" data-end="286">tr.ee</code> não deixam eu ver o @ daqui) ✅</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="321" data-end="385">E eu já preparei os arquivos certinhos pra você subir no GitHub.</p>
<h2 data-start="387" data-end="416">Baixar os arquivos prontos</h2>
<ul data-start="417" data-end="662">
<li data-start="417" data-end="546">
<p data-start="419" data-end="546"><span class="" data-state="closed"><a data-start="419" data-end="506" class="cursor-pointer">Cartilha (PDF) pronta pra colocar no site</a></span> <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="relative inline-flex items-center"><button class="ms-1 flex h-[25px] text-[10px] leading-[13px] rounded-xl corner-superellipse/1.1 items-center justify-center gap-1 px-2 relative text-token-text-secondary! hover:text-token-text-primary! hover:bg-token-bg-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary dark:hover:bg-token-bg-secondary bg-[#f4f4f4] "><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="h-[16px] w-[16px] object-contain text-token-text-primary! flex-none icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#554074" fill="currentColor"></use></svg><p class="not-prose mt-0! mb-0! flex-auto truncate">Cartilha (2)</p></button></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-start="547" data-end="662">
<p data-start="549" data-end="662"><span class="" data-state="closed"><a data-start="549" data-end="622" class="cursor-pointer">Capa da cartilha (imagem clicável)</a></span> <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="relative inline-flex items-center"><button class="ms-1 flex h-[25px] text-[10px] leading-[13px] rounded-xl corner-superellipse/1.1 items-center justify-center gap-1 px-2 relative text-token-text-secondary! hover:text-token-text-primary! hover:bg-token-bg-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary dark:hover:bg-token-bg-secondary bg-[#f4f4f4] "><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="h-[16px] w-[16px] object-contain text-token-text-primary! flex-none icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#554074" fill="currentColor"></use></svg><p class="not-prose mt-0! mb-0! flex-auto truncate">Cartilha (2)</p></button></span></span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<blockquote data-start="664" data-end="805">
<p data-start="666" data-end="805">A capa foi tirada da <strong data-start="687" data-end="699">página 1</strong> da sua cartilha (“Bem-estar Felino – Técnicas de Manejo Amigável”). <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="relative inline-flex items-center"><button class="ms-1 flex h-[25px] text-[10px] leading-[13px] rounded-xl corner-superellipse/1.1 items-center justify-center gap-1 px-2 relative text-token-text-secondary! hover:text-token-text-primary! hover:bg-token-bg-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary dark:hover:bg-token-bg-secondary bg-[#f4f4f4] "><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="h-[16px] w-[16px] object-contain text-token-text-primary! flex-none icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#554074" fill="currentColor"></use></svg><p class="not-prose mt-0! mb-0! flex-auto truncate">Cartilha (2)</p></button></span></span></p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="807" data-end="810">
<h2 data-start="812" data-end="856">O que você vai fazer no GitHub (3 passos)</h2>
<h3 data-start="858" data-end="885">1) Subir o PDF e a capa</h3>
<p data-start="886" data-end="905">No seu repositório:</p>
<ul data-start="906" data-end="1066">
<li data-start="906" data-end="935">
<p data-start="908" data-end="935"><strong data-start="908" data-end="935">Add file → Upload files</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="936" data-end="1045">
<p data-start="938" data-end="990">Envie esses 2 arquivos com esses nomes (igualzinho):</p>
<ul data-start="993" data-end="1045">
<li data-start="993" data-end="1021">
<p data-start="995" data-end="1021"><code data-start="995" data-end="1021">cartilha-catfriendly.pdf</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1024" data-end="1045">
<p data-start="1026" data-end="1045"><code data-start="1026" data-end="1045">cartilha-capa.png</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="1046" data-end="1066">
<p data-start="1048" data-end="1066"><strong data-start="1048" data-end="1066">Commit changes</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="1068" data-end="1099">2) Atualizar o <code data-start="1087" data-end="1099">index.html</code></h3>
<ul data-start="1100" data-end="1263">
<li data-start="1100" data-end="1129">
<p data-start="1102" data-end="1129">Abra <code data-start="1107" data-end="1119">index.html</code> → ✏️ Edit</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1130" data-end="1146">
<p data-start="1132" data-end="1146"><strong data-start="1132" data-end="1146">apaga tudo</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1147" data-end="1225">
<p data-start="1149" data-end="1225">copia <strong data-start="1155" data-end="1191">todo o código que está no canvas</strong> (o site no formato da sua imagem)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1226" data-end="1242">
<p data-start="1228" data-end="1242">cola no GitHub</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1243" data-end="1263">
<p data-start="1245" data-end="1263"><strong data-start="1245" data-end="1263">Commit changes</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="1265" data-end="1307">3) Ajustar nomes e @ dos profissionais</h3>
<p data-start="1308" data-end="1364">Na seção <strong data-start="1317" data-end="1343">“Nossos Profissionais”</strong>, você vai ver assim:</p>
<ul data-start="1366" data-end="1669">
<li data-start="1366" data-end="1418">
<p data-start="1368" data-end="1418"><strong data-start="1368" data-end="1386">Profissional 1</strong><br data-start="1386" data-end="1389">
<code data-start="1391" data-end="1418">@coloque_o_instagram_aqui</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1419" data-end="1471">
<p data-start="1421" data-end="1471"><strong data-start="1421" data-end="1439">Profissional 2</strong><br data-start="1439" data-end="1442">
<code data-start="1444" data-end="1471">@coloque_o_instagram_aqui</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1472" data-end="1521">
<p data-start="1474" data-end="1521"><strong data-start="1474" data-end="1519">Isabelle Guimarães — @isaguimaraes.catvet</strong> ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1522" data-end="1574">
<p data-start="1524" data-end="1574"><strong data-start="1524" data-end="1542">Profissional 3</strong><br data-start="1542" data-end="1545">
<code data-start="1547" data-end="1574">@coloque_o_instagram_aqui</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1575" data-end="1627">
<p data-start="1577" data-end="1627"><strong data-start="1577" data-end="1595">Profissional 4</strong><br data-start="1595" data-end="1598">
<code data-start="1600" data-end="1627">@coloque_o_instagram_aqui</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1628" data-end="1669">
<p data-start="1630" data-end="1669"><strong data-start="1630" data-end="1667">Cats Academy BR — @cats_academybr</strong> ✅</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1671" data-end="1758">📌 Você só troca “Profissional 1/2/3/4” pelo <strong data-start="1716" data-end="1724">nome</strong> e troca o <code data-start="1735" data-end="1741">@...</code> pelo <strong data-start="1747" data-end="1757">@ real</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1760" data-end="1910">Se você me mandar aqui <strong data-start="1783" data-end="1799">os nomes + @</strong> desses 4 (pode ser só em lista), eu já deixo tudo preenchido por você no site sem você precisar mexer em nada.</p>
<hr data-start="1912" data-end="1915">
<p data-start="1917" data-end="2069">Se quiser também, eu ajusto já o botão <strong data-start="1956" data-end="1968">WhatsApp</strong> e o <strong data-start="1973" data-end="1982">Email</strong> (na seção Contatos) — é só você me dizer o número e o e-mail oficiais do projeto/LAMF.</p>
