der-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="0e64a7f5-cc36-42cf-9ddb-9bd74060ea59" data-testid="conversation-turn-88" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only">O ChatGPT disse:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="1302253d-8b2f-4737-a95a-e5a45e798980" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="187">PERFEITO 😍 ficou exatamente no nível que um <strong data-start="45" data-end="59">PROEX pede</strong>.<br data-start="60" data-end="63">
Agora vamos fazer a <strong data-start="83" data-end="107">última parte prática</strong>, bem simples, pra esses avatares <strong data-start="141" data-end="186">aparecerem certinhos em cada profissional</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="189" data-end="192">
<h2 data-start="194" data-end="243">1️⃣ Primeiro: separar os avatares (mapeamento)</h2>
<p data-start="244" data-end="326">Da imagem que você aprovou, vamos usar <strong data-start="283" data-end="318">1 avatar para cada profissional</strong>, assim:</p>
<h3 data-start="328" data-end="346">👩‍⚕️ Mulheres</h3>
<ul data-start="347" data-end="704">
<li data-start="347" data-end="444">
<p data-start="349" data-end="444"><strong data-start="349" data-end="372">Dra. Bruna Oliveira</strong> → avatar feminina com gato cinza<br data-start="405" data-end="408">
👉 salvar como: <code data-start="426" data-end="444">avatar-bruna.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="445" data-end="526">
<p data-start="447" data-end="526"><strong data-start="447" data-end="467">Dra. Érica Baffa</strong> → avatar feminina com gato claro<br data-start="500" data-end="503">
👉 <code data-start="508" data-end="526">avatar-erica.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="527" data-end="615">
<p data-start="529" data-end="615"><strong data-start="529" data-end="551">Isabelle Guimarães</strong> → avatar feminina com gato laranja<br data-start="586" data-end="589">
👉 <code data-start="594" data-end="615">avatar-isabelle.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="616" data-end="704">
<p data-start="618" data-end="704"><strong data-start="618" data-end="636">Heloisa Justen</strong> → avatar feminina (pode repetir estilo)<br data-start="676" data-end="679">
👉 <code data-start="684" data-end="704">avatar-heloisa.png</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="706" data-end="738">👨‍⚕️ Homens / Institucional</h3>
<ul data-start="739" data-end="917">
<li data-start="739" data-end="829">
<p data-start="741" data-end="829"><strong data-start="741" data-end="765">Dr. Alexandre Daniel</strong> → avatar masculino com gato preto<br data-start="799" data-end="802">
👉 <code data-start="807" data-end="829">avatar-alexandre.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="830" data-end="917">
<p data-start="832" data-end="917"><strong data-start="832" data-end="851">Cats Academy BR</strong> → avatar masculino com gato cinza<br data-start="885" data-end="888">
👉 <code data-start="893" data-end="917">avatar-catsacademy.png</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="919" data-end="1034">📌 <strong data-start="922" data-end="937">Importante:</strong><br data-start="937" data-end="940">
Os nomes dos arquivos <strong data-start="962" data-end="995">precisam ser exatamente esses</strong>, porque o HTML já está esperando eles.</p>
<hr data-start="1036" data-end="1039">
<h2 data-start="1041" data-end="1091">2️⃣ O que você precisa fazer agora (bem rápido)</h2>
<h3 data-start="1092" data-end="1127">🔹 Passo A — baixar os avatares</h3>
<ul data-start="1128" data-end="1247">
<li data-start="1128" data-end="1161">
<p data-start="1130" data-end="1161">Salva a imagem que você aprovou</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1162" data-end="1194">
<p data-start="1164" data-end="1194">Recorta cada avatar (quadrado)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1195" data-end="1247">
<p data-start="1197" data-end="1247">Salva com os nomes acima (<code data-start="1223" data-end="1241">avatar-bruna.png</code> etc.)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="1249" data-end="1281">🔹 Passo B — subir no GitHub</h3>
<p data-start="1282" data-end="1318">No repositório <strong data-start="1297" data-end="1317">catfriendly-site</strong>:</p>
<ol data-start="1319" data-end="1579">
<li data-start="1319" data-end="1344">
