</li>
<li data-start="1345" data-end="1364">
<p data-start="1348" data-end="1364"><strong data-start="1348" data-end="1364">Upload files</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1365" data-end="1547">
<p data-start="1368" data-end="1388">Envie os 6 arquivos:</p>
