<hr data-start="421" data-end="424">
<h2 data-start="426" data-end="470">1️⃣ Entenda como o site “acha” as imagens</h2>
<p data-start="471" data-end="508">No seu código, por exemplo, tem isso:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="510" data-end="576"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">img</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">src</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"avatar-bruna.png"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">alt</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Dra. Bruna Oliveira"</span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="578" data-end="700">Isso significa:<br>
➡️ O site procura um arquivo chamado <strong data-start="631" data-end="651">avatar-bruna.png</strong><br data-start="651" data-end="654">
➡️ <strong data-start="657" data-end="700">no mesmo lugar onde está o <code data-start="686" data-end="698">index.html</code></strong></p>
<p data-start="702" data-end="754">Se o arquivo não existir ali → a imagem não aparece.</p>
<hr data-start="756" data-end="759">
<h2 data-start="761" data-end="808">2️⃣ Primeiro: salvar as imagens corretamente</h2>
<p data-start="809" data-end="838">No seu celular ou computador:</p>
<p data-start="840" data-end="928">Salve <strong data-start="846" data-end="865">cada bonequinho</strong> com <strong data-start="870" data-end="896">EXATAMENTE estes nomes</strong><br data-start="896" data-end="899">
(copia e cola pra não errar):</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="930" data-end="1054"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1"></div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>avatar-bruna.png
avatar-erica.png
avatar-isabelle.png
avatar-heloisa.png
avatar-alexandre.png
avatar-catsacademy.png
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1056" data-end="1067">⚠️ Atenção:</p>
<ul data-start="1068" data-end="1130">
<li data-start="1068" data-end="1084">
<p data-start="1070" data-end="1084">tudo minúsculo</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1085" data-end="1097">
<p data-start="1087" data-end="1097">sem espaço</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1098" data-end="1110">
<p data-start="1100" data-end="1110">sem acento</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1111" data-end="1130">
<p data-start="1113" data-end="1130">termina em <code data-start="1124" data-end="1130">.png</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1132" data-end="1135">
<h2 data-start="1137" data-end="1193">3️⃣ Agora: subir as imagens no GitHub (passo a passo)</h2>
<p data-start="1194" data-end="1230">No repositório <strong data-start="1209" data-end="1229">catfriendly-site</strong>:</p>
<h3 data-start="1232" data-end="1246">🔹 Passo 1</h3>
<p data-start="1247" data-end="1269">Clique em <strong data-start="1257" data-end="1269">Add file</strong></p>
<h3 data-start="1271" data-end="1285">🔹 Passo 2</h3>
<p data-start="1286" data-end="1312">Clique em <strong data-start="1296" data-end="1312">Upload files</strong></p>
<h3 data-start="1314" data-end="1328">🔹 Passo 3</h3>
<p data-start="1329" data-end="1354">Arraste TODAS as imagens:</p>
<ul data-start="1355" data-end="1469">
<li data-start="1355" data-end="1376">
<p data-start="1357" data-end="1376">os 6 <code data-start="1362" data-end="1376">avatar-*.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1377" data-end="1419">
<p data-start="1379" data-end="1419"><code data-start="1379" data-end="1398">cartilha-capa.png</code> (se ainda não subiu)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1420" data-end="1469">
<p data-start="1422" data-end="1469"><code data-start="1422" data-end="1448">cartilha-catfriendly.pdf</code> (se ainda não subiu)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="1471" data-end="1485">🔹 Passo 4</h3>
<p data-start="1486" data-end="1555">Role a página para baixo<br data-start="1510" data-end="1513">
Clique em <strong data-start="1523" data-end="1541">Commit changes</strong> (botão verde)</p>
<p data-start="1557" data-end="1573">Pronto. Só isso.</p>
<hr data-start="1575" data-end="1578">
<h2 data-start="1580" data-end="1608">4️⃣ O que acontece depois</h2>
