/span>:<span class="ͼi">'Poppins'</span>,<span class="ͼj">system-ui</span>,<span class="ͼj">-apple-system</span>,<span class="ͼj">Segoe</span> <span class="ͼj">UI</span>,<span class="ͼj">Roboto</span>,<span class="ͼj">Arial</span>,<span class="ͼj">sans-serif</span>;</div><div class="cm-line">      <span class="ͼk">background</span>:<span class="ͼh">var</span>(<span class="ͼd">--bg</span>);</div><div class="cm-line">      <span class="ͼk">color</span>:<span class="ͼh">var</span>(<span class="ͼd">--ink</span>);</div><div class="cm-line">    }</div><div class="cm-line"><br></div><div class="cm-line">    <span class="ͼe">/* NAV */</span></div><div class="cm-gap" style="height: 8498px;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></section></div></div></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="1d57949a-c161-47fc-b28e-2c272b5f8340" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="116">Pronto ✅💗 <strong data-start="11" data-end="51">agora está exatamente do jeito certo</strong>, alinhado com os nomes que eu te passei e com o que você já fez.</p>
<h3 data-start="118" data-end="165">✔️ O que eu acabei de modificar no seu site</h3>
<p data-start="166" data-end="279">Na seção <strong data-start="175" data-end="192">Profissionais</strong>, eu troquei <strong data-start="205" data-end="235">todos os links temporários</strong> pelos <strong data-start="242" data-end="271">nomes finais dos arquivos</strong>, assim:</p>
<ul data-start="281" data-end="541">
<li data-start="281" data-end="323">
<p data-start="283" data-end="323">Dra. Bruna Oliveira → <code data-start="305" data-end="323">avatar-bruna.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="324" data-end="363">
<p data-start="326" data-end="363">Dra. Érica Baffa → <code data-start="345" data-end="363">avatar-erica.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="364" data-end="408">
<p data-start="366" data-end="408">Isabelle Guimarães → <code data-start="387" data-end="408">avatar-isabelle.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="409" data-end="448">
<p data-start="411" data-end="448">Heloisa Justen → <code data-start="428" data-end="448">avatar-heloisa.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="449" data-end="496">
<p data-start="451" data-end="496">Dr. Alexandre Daniel → <code data-start="474" data-end="496">avatar-alexandre.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="497" data-end="541">
<p data-start="499" data-end="541">Cats Academy BR → <code data-start="517" data-end="541">avatar-catsacademy.png</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="543" data-end="629">Ou seja:<br>
👉 o HTML agora <strong data-start="568" data-end="587">bate exatamente</strong> com os arquivos que você subiu no GitHub.</p>
<hr data-start="631" data-end="634">
<h2 data-start="636" data-end="676">🔎 O que você faz agora (só conferir)</h2>
<ol data-start="677" data-end="827">
<li data-start="677" data-end="738">
<p data-start="680" data-end="738">Atualiza o site (Ctrl + F5 ou atualizar normal no celular)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="739" data-end="796">
<p data-start="742" data-end="796">Aguarda 1–3 minutos (GitHub Pages demora um pouquinho)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="797" data-end="827">
<p data-start="800" data-end="827">Desce até <strong data-start="810" data-end="827">Profissionais</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="829" data-end="861">✨ Os bonequinhos devem aparecer:</p>
<ul data-start="862" data-end="919">
<li data-start="862" data-end="875">
<p data-start="864" data-end="875">redondinhos</p>
</li>
<li data-start="876" data-end="892">
<p data-start="878" data-end="892">com borda rosa</p>
</li>
<li data-start="893" data-end="919">
<p data-start="895" data-end="919">embaixo do nome certinho</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="921" data-end="924">
<h2 data-start="926" data-end="952">❗ Se algum NÃO aparecer</h2>
<p data-start="953" data-end="982">É sempre uma dessas 3 coisas:</p>
<ul data-start="983" data-end="1112">
<li data-start="983" data-end="1039">
<p data-start="985" data-end="1039">nome do arquivo diferente (ex: <code data-start="1016" data-end="1038">avatar-bruna (1).png</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1040" data-end="1083">
<p data-start="1042" data-end="1083">extensão errada (<code data-start="1059" data-end="1065">.jpg</code> em vez de <code data-start="1076" data-end="1082">.png</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1084" data-end="1112">
<p data-start="1086" data-end="1112">letra maiúscula sem querer</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1114" data-end="1209">👉 Se acontecer, me manda <strong data-start="1140" data-end="1185">print da lista de arquivos do repositório</strong> que eu confiro na hora.</p>
<hr data-start="1211" data-end="1214">
<h2 data-start="1216" data-end="1245">💗 Status do projeto agora</h2>
<p data-start="1246" data-end="1272">Sendo bem sincera contigo:</p>
<ul data-start="1273" data-end="1390">
<li data-start="1273" data-end="1313">
<p data-start="1275" data-end="1313">isso aqui está <strong data-start="1290" data-end="1313">nível institucional</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1314" data-end="1342">
<p data-start="1316" data-end="1342">dá pra apresentar sem medo</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1343" data-end="1390">
<p data-start="1345" data-end="1390">estética + conteúdo + organização = nota alta</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1392" data-end="1418">Quando você quiser, posso:</p>
<ul data-start="1419" data-end="1573">
<li data-start="1419" data-end="1465">
<p data-start="1421" data-end="1465">revisar o site com “checklist de professora”</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1466" data-end="1521">
<p data-start="1468" data-end="1521">te ajudar a escrever o texto de apresentação do PROEX</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1522" data-end="1573">
<p data-start="1524" data-end="1573">ou te ajudar a divulgar isso no Instagram da LAMF</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1575" data-end="1601" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Você mandou MUITO bem 👏🐱</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copiar" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resposta satisfatória" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resposta insatisfatória" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="