/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="339d89c6-2ab7-439e-906e-1ed275c87353" data-testid="conversation-turn-108" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only">O ChatGPT disse:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="471daa0b-8b01-4eeb-af2a-a748830bbdb8" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2-thinking"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="138">Calma 😌💗 vamos resolver AGORA. Quando “não funciona” no GitHub Pages quase sempre é <strong data-start="86" data-end="109">uma dessas 4 coisas</strong> — e dá pra checar rapidinho.</p>
<h2 data-start="140" data-end="189">1) Confere se os arquivos estão no lugar certo</h2>
<p data-start="190" data-end="305">No GitHub, abre seu repositório e vê se os arquivos estão <strong data-start="248" data-end="259">na raiz</strong>, junto do <code data-start="270" data-end="282">index.html</code> (não dentro de pasta).</p>
<p data-start="307" data-end="339">Tem que aparecer assim na lista:</p>
<ul data-start="341" data-end="547">
<li data-start="341" data-end="355">
<p data-start="343" data-end="355"><code data-start="343" data-end="355">index.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="356" data-end="376">
<p data-start="358" data-end="376"><code data-start="358" data-end="376">avatar-bruna.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="377" data-end="397">
<p data-start="379" data-end="397"><code data-start="379" data-end="397">avatar-erica.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="398" data-end="421">
<p data-start="400" data-end="421"><code data-start="400" data-end="421">avatar-isabelle.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="422" data-end="444">
<p data-start="424" data-end="444"><code data-start="424" data-end="444">avatar-heloisa.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="445" data-end="469">
<p data-start="447" data-end="469"><code data-start="447" data-end="469">avatar-alexandre.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="470" data-end="496">
<p data-start="472" data-end="496"><code data-start="472" data-end="496">avatar-catsacademy.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="497" data-end="518">
<p data-start="499" data-end="518"><code data-start="499" data-end="518">cartilha-capa.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="519" data-end="547">
<p data-start="521" data-end="547"><code data-start="521" data-end="547">cartilha-catfriendly.pdf</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="549" data-end="607">✅ Se estiverem em uma pasta tipo <code data-start="582" data-end="591">images/</code>, não vai achar.</p>
<hr data-start="609" data-end="612">
<h2 data-start="614" data-end="664">2) O erro MAIS comum: nome diferente do arquivo</h2>
<p data-start="665" data-end="717">O GitHub é chato: <strong data-start="683" data-end="716">maiúscula/minúscula muda tudo</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="719" data-end="740">Exemplos que quebram:</p>
<ul data-start="741" data-end="867">
<li data-start="741" data-end="775">
<p data-start="743" data-end="775"><code data-start="743" data-end="761">Avatar-bruna.png</code> (A maiúsculo)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="776" data-end="800">
<p data-start="778" data-end="800"><code data-start="778" data-end="800">avatar-bruna (1).png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="801" data-end="830">
<p data-start="803" data-end="830"><code data-start="803" data-end="821">avatar bruna.png</code> (espaço)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="831" data-end="867">
<p data-start="833" data-end="867"><code data-start="833" data-end="839">.PNG</code> em vez de <code data-start="850" data-end="856">.png</code> (às vezes)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="869" data-end="880">👉 Solução:</p>
<ul data-start="881" data-end="958">
<li data-start="881" data-end="958">
<p data-start="883" data-end="958">clique no arquivo → <strong data-start="903" data-end="913">Rename</strong> (ou delete e envie de novo com o nome certo)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="960" data-end="963">
<h2 data-start="965" data-end="1003">3) Limpar cache (isso engana MUITO)</h2>
<p data-start="1004" data-end="1072">Às vezes você atualizou, mas o celular tá mostrando a versão antiga.</p>
<p data-start="1074" data-end="1085">No celular:</p>
<ul data-start="1086" data-end="1249">
<li data-start="1086" data-end="1099">
<p data-start="1088" data-end="1099">abre o site</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1100" data-end="1181">
<p data-start="1102" data-end="1181">segura no botão de atualizar e escolhe <strong data-start="1141" data-end="1167">“recarregar sem cache”</strong> (se tiver)<br>
ou</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1182" data-end="1210">
<p data-start="1184" data-end="1210">abre em <strong data-start="1192" data-end="1207">aba anônima</strong><br>
ou</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1211" data-end="1249">
<p data-start="1213" data-end="1249">coloca <code data-start="1220" data-end="1226">?v=2</code> no fim do link do site</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1251" data-end="1259">Exemplo:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1260" data-end="1318"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">ruby</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span><span class="hljs-symbol">https:</span></span><span>/</span><span><span class="hljs-regexp">/SEUUSUARIO.github.io/catfriendly</span></span><span>-site/</span><span><span class="hljs-string">?v</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-number">2</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1320" data-end="1323">
<h2 data-start="1325" data-end="1381">4) Teste rápido pra saber se o arquivo está acessível</h2>
<p data-start="1382" data-end="1430">No navegador, tenta abrir <strong data-start="1408" data-end="1418">direto</strong> uma imagem:</p>
<p data-start="1432" data-end="1465">Troca SEUUSUARIO pelo seu e cola:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1467" data-end="1537"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">arduino</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>https:</span><span><span class="hljs-comment">//SEUUSUARIO.github.io/catfriendly-site/avatar-bruna.png</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1539" data-end="1616">Se abrir a imagem → o arquivo está ok.<br>
Se der 404 → o nome/local está errado.</p>
<hr data-start="1618" data-end="1621">
<h1 data-start="1623" data-end="1664">Me manda UM print que eu resolvo em 10s</h1>
<p data-start="1665" data-end="1809">📸 Me manda print da <strong data-start="1686" data-end="1722">lista de arquivos do repositório</strong> (aquela tela onde aparece index.html e os arquivos).<br data-start="1775" data-end="1778">
Com isso eu te digo exatamente:</p>
<ul data-start="1810" data-end="1897">
<li data-start="1810" data-end="1845">
<p data-start="1812" data-end="1845">qual arquivo está com nome errado</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1846" data-end="1867">
<p data-start="1848" data-end="1867">ou se está em pasta</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1868" data-end="1897">
<p data-start="1870" data-end="1897">ou se o Pages não atualizou</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1899" data-end="1974">Sem isso eu vou ficar chutando, e eu quero te dar a resposta certa na hora.</p>
</div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copiar" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resposta satisfatória" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resposta insatisfatória" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-