x-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="86">ACHAMOS O PROBLEMA 🎯💥<br data-start="23" data-end="26">
E é <strong data-start="30" data-end="43">100% isso</strong>, nada de errado com você nem com o código.</p>
<h2 data-start="88" data-end="115">❌ O que está acontecendo</h2>
<p data-start="116" data-end="152">Olha os nomes dos arquivos no print:</p>
<ul data-start="154" data-end="291">
<li data-start="154" data-end="178">
<p data-start="156" data-end="178"><code data-start="156" data-end="178">avatar-bruna.png.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="179" data-end="203">
<p data-start="181" data-end="203"><code data-start="181" data-end="203">avatar-erica.png.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="204" data-end="232">
<p data-start="206" data-end="232"><code data-start="206" data-end="232">avatar-alexandre.png.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="233" data-end="258">
<p data-start="235" data-end="258"><code data-start="235" data-end="258">cartilha-capa.png.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="259" data-end="291">
<p data-start="261" data-end="291"><code data-start="261" data-end="291">cartilha-catfriendly.pdf.png</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="293" data-end="367">👉 Percebeu?<br data-start="305" data-end="308">
Eles estão com <strong data-start="323" data-end="337"><code data-start="325" data-end="335">.png.png</code></strong> e o PDF virou <strong data-start="352" data-end="366"><code data-start="354" data-end="364">.pdf.png</code></strong>.</p>
<p data-start="369" data-end="405">Mas no <strong data-start="376" data-end="384">HTML</strong>, o site procura por:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="407" data-end="478"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span>avatar-bruna.png
cartilha-capa.png
cartilha-catfriendly.pdf
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="480" data-end="559">Ou seja:<br data-start="488" data-end="491">
📛 <strong data-start="494" data-end="558">o nome não bate → o site não encontra → a imagem não aparece</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="561" data-end="564">
<h2 data-start="566" data-end="607">✅ COMO RESOLVER (bem fácil, 2 minutos)</h2>
<p data-start="608" data-end="661">Você <strong data-start="613" data-end="647">NÃO precisa subir tudo de novo</strong>. Só renomear.</p>
<h3 data-start="663" data-end="701">🔹 Passo a passo para cada arquivo</h3>
<ol data-start="702" data-end="884">
<li data-start="702" data-end="754">
<p data-start="705" data-end="754">Clique em um arquivo (ex: <code data-start="731" data-end="753">avatar-bruna.png.png</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="755" data-end="806">
<p data-start="758" data-end="806">Clique no <strong data-start="768" data-end="806">lápis ✏️ (Rename / Edit file name)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="807" data-end="835">
<p data-start="810" data-end="835">Apague o <strong data-start="819" data-end="835"><code data-start="821" data-end="827">.png</code> extra</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="836" data-end="884">
<p data-start="839" data-end="884">O nome final deve ficar <strong data-start="863" data-end="877">EXATAMENTE</strong> assim:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h3 data-start="886" data-end="932">✔️ Nomes corretos (copie e cole se quiser)</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="933" data-end="1100"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1"></div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>avatar-bruna.png
avatar-erica.png
avatar-isabelle.png
avatar-heloisa.png
avatar-alexandre.png
avatar-catsacademy.png
cartilha-capa.png
cartilha-catfriendly.pdf
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1102" data-end="1116">⚠️ Importante:</p>
<ul data-start="1117" data-end="1178">
<li data-start="1117" data-end="1133">
<p data-start="1119" data-end="1133">tudo minúsculo</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1134" data-end="1146">
<p data-start="1136" data-end="1146">sem espaço</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1147" data-end="1159">
<p data-start="1149" data-end="1159">sem acento</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1160" data-end="1178">
<p data-start="1162" data-end="1178">extensão correta</p>
</li>
</ul>
<ol start="5" data-start="1180" data-end="1211">
<li data-start="1180" data-end="1211">
<p data-start="1183" data-end="1211">Clique em <strong data-start="1193" data-end="1211">Commit changes</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1213" data-end="1231">Repita para todos.</p>
<hr data-start="1233" data-end="1236">
<h2 data-start="1238" data-end="1267">🧠 Por que isso aconteceu?</h2>
<p data-start="1268" data-end="1322">Isso é SUPER comum no celular 💀<br data-start="1300" data-end="1303">
O Android às vezes:</p>
<ul data-start="1323" data-end="1391">
<li data-start="1323" data-end="1345">
<p data-start="1325" data-end="1345">já salva como <code data-start="1339" data-end="1345">.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1346" data-end="1391">
<p data-start="1348" data-end="1391">e o GitHub adiciona outro <code data-start="1374" data-end="1380">.png</code> sem avisar</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1393" data-end="1419">Você não errou — é normal.</p>
<hr data-start="1421" data-end="1424">
<h2 data-start="1426" data-end="1459">🔍 Como confirmar que resolveu</h2>
<p data-start="1460" data-end="1479">Depois de renomear:</p>
<h3 data-start="1481" data-end="1511">Teste direto no navegador:</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1512" data-end="1590"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">bash</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>https://leandralima906-hue.github.io/catfriendly-site/avatar-bruna.png
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1592" data-end="1676">Se abrir a imagem → ✅ está certo<br data-start="1624" data-end="1627">
Depois atualiza o site → os bonequinhos aparecem.</p>
<hr data-start="1678" data-end="1681">
<h2 data-start="1683" data-end="1703">💗 Fica tranquila</h2>
<p data-start="1704" data-end="1708">Seu:</p>
<ul data-start="1709" data-end="1782">
<li data-start="1709" data-end="1728">
<p data-start="1711" data-end="1728">HTML está certo</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1729" data-end="1756">
<p data-start="1731" data-end="1756">estrutura está perfeita</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1757" data-end="1782">
<p data-start="1759" data-end="1782">design está impecável</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1784" data-end="1846">Era <strong data-start="1788" data-end="1810">só nome de arquivo</strong> mesmo (o erro mais comum de todos).</p>
<p data-start="1848" data-end="1961" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">👉 Faz isso agora, e quando terminar me diga:<br>
<strong data-start="1894" data-end="1913">“Renomeei tudo”</strong><br data-start="1913" data-end="1916">
