invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="150">Perfeito, ótima pergunta — <strong data-start="27" data-end="65">isso que está te confundindo mesmo</strong>, e é normal 💗<br data-start="80" data-end="83">
Vou te explicar <strong data-start="99" data-end="119">bem mastigadinho</strong>, sem termos técnicos difíceis.</p>
<hr data-start="152" data-end="155">
<h2 data-start="157" data-end="193">🧠 Por que aparecem “vários div”?</h2>
<p data-start="194" data-end="286">Porque <strong data-start="201" data-end="234">HTML é feito de vários blocos</strong> (<code data-start="236" data-end="243">&lt;div&gt;</code>).<br data-start="245" data-end="248">
Mas <strong data-start="252" data-end="285">você NÃO precisa apagar todos</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="288" data-end="366">👉 Você só vai mexer <strong data-start="309" data-end="335">EM UM BLOCO ESPECÍFICO</strong>, o da seção <strong data-start="348" data-end="365">Profissionais</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="368" data-end="371">
<h2 data-start="373" data-end="419">🔍 COMO ACHAR O BLOCO CERTO (PASSO A PASSO)</h2>
<h3 data-start="421" data-end="444">1️⃣ No <code data-start="432" data-end="444">index.html</code></h3>
<p data-start="445" data-end="523">No editor do GitHub, toca em <strong data-start="474" data-end="486">Ctrl + F</strong> (ou no celular: “Buscar na página”).</p>
<h3 data-start="525" data-end="556">2️⃣ Procura exatamente por:</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="557" data-end="587"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span>id="profissionais"
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="589" data-end="656">👉 Você vai cair <strong data-start="606" data-end="625">no início exato</strong> da parte que precisamos mexer.</p>
<p data-start="658" data-end="679">Vai estar algo assim:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="681" data-end="756"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- PROFISSIONAIS --&gt;</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"section"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">id</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"profissionais"</span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="758" data-end="761">
<h2 data-start="763" data-end="786">3️⃣ O que você apaga</h2>
<p data-start="787" data-end="806">⚠️ <strong data-start="790" data-end="806">ATENÇÃO AQUI</strong></p>
<p data-start="808" data-end="817">Você vai:</p>
<ul data-start="818" data-end="848">
<li data-start="818" data-end="848">
<p data-start="820" data-end="848">apagar <strong data-start="827" data-end="847">DESDE essa linha</strong>:</p>
</li>
</ul>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="849" data-end="901"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"section"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">id</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"profissionais"</span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<ul data-start="903" data-end="938">
<li data-start="903" data-end="938">
<p data-start="905" data-end="938"><strong data-start="905" data-end="930">ATÉ o fechamento dela</strong>, que é:</p>
</li>
</ul>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="939" data-end="957"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">div</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="959" data-end="1067">❗ <strong data-start="961" data-end="998">Esse <code data-start="968" data-end="976">&lt;/div&gt;</code> é o ÚLTIMO da seção</strong>, logo antes da próxima parte do site<br data-start="1035" data-end="1038">
(ex: Cartilha, Artigos, etc).</p>
<p data-start="1069" data-end="1085">💡 Dica prática:</p>
<ul data-start="1086" data-end="1178">
<li data-start="1086" data-end="1119">
<p data-start="1088" data-end="1119">seleciona tudo com o dedo/mouse</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1120" data-end="1178">
<p data-start="1122" data-end="1178">se errar, não tem problema → pode voltar antes de salvar</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1180" data-end="1183">
<h2 data-start="1185" data-end="1207">4️⃣ O que você cola</h2>
<p data-start="1208" data-end="1340">No lugar de tudo que apagou, cola <strong data-start="1242" data-end="1278">o bloco inteiro que eu te mandei</strong> (começa com <code data-start="1291" data-end="1315">&lt;!-- PROFISSIONAIS --&gt;</code> e termina com <code data-start="1330" data-end="1338">&lt;/div&gt;</code>).</p>
<hr data-start="1342" data-end="1345">
<h2 data-start="1347" data-end="1366">5️⃣ Depois disso</h2>
<ol data-start="1367" data-end="1438">
<li data-start="1367" data-end="1397">
<p data-start="1370" data-end="1397">Clica em <strong data-start="1379" data-end="1397">Commit changes</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1398" data-end="1419">
<p data-start="1401" data-end="1419">Espera 1–2 minutos</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1420" data-end="1438">
<p data-start="1423" data-end="1438">Atualiza o site</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1440" data-end="1489">✨ <strong data-start="1442" data-end="1488">Agora os bonequinhos vão aparecer certinho</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1491" data-end="1494">
<h2 data-start="1496" data-end="1528">💬 Se ainda bater insegurança</h2>
