      &lt;h2&gt;Artigos, Revistas e Consensos&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Materiais selecionados para estudo e apoio à prática Cat Friendly.&lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;div class="divider"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;div class="list"&gt;
      &lt;div class="item"&gt;&lt;span class="bullet" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://revistas.faa.edu.br/SaberDigital/article/view/1595" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Saber Digital (FAA) — artigo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="item"&gt;&lt;span class="bullet" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.catslondrina.com.br/bem-estar/como-levar-seu-gato-no-veterinario-sem-estresse-ou-trauma-um-guia-passo-a-passo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Guia: levar o gato ao veterinário sem estresse&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="item"&gt;&lt;span class="bullet" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/36259500/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;PubMed — artigo (36259500)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="item"&gt;&lt;span class="bullet" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://portalvet.royalcanin.com.br/saude-e-nutricao/nutricao/importancia-da-agua-para-felinos/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Royal Canin: importância da água para felinos&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="item"&gt;&lt;span class="bullet" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.petlove.com.br/dicas/lugares-que-voce-deve-fazer-carinho-gato" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Petlove: lugares para fazer carinho no gato&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="item"&gt;&lt;span class="bullet" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://downloads.editoracientifica.com.br/articles/220910108.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;PDF — Editora Científica&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="item"&gt;&lt;span class="bullet" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://lume.ufrgs.br/handle/10183/170364" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;UFRGS (Lume) — trabalho acadêmico&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

