<hr data-start="2584" data-end="2587">
<h3 data-start="2589" data-end="2621">🔥 Importante (pra aparecer)</h3>
<p data-start="2622" data-end="2696">Os nomes dos arquivos no GitHub precisam ser <strong data-start="2667" data-end="2677">iguais</strong> a esses do código:</p>
<ul data-start="2697" data-end="2837">
<li data-start="2697" data-end="2717">
<p data-start="2699" data-end="2717"><code data-start="2699" data-end="2717">avatar-bruna.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2718" data-end="2738">
<p data-start="2720" data-end="2738"><code data-start="2720" data-end="2738">avatar-erica.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2739" data-end="2762">
<p data-start="2741" data-end="2762"><code data-start="2741" data-end="2762">avatar-isabelle.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2763" data-end="2785">
<p data-start="2765" data-end="2785"><code data-start="2765" data-end="2785">avatar-heloisa.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2786" data-end="2810">
<p data-start="2788" data-end="2810"><code data-start="2788" data-end="2810">avatar-alexandre.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2811" data-end="2837">
<p data-start="2813" data-end="2837"><code data-start="2813" data-end="2837">avatar-catsacademy.png</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2839" data-end="2916">Se no seu repositório estiver com <code data-start="2873" data-end="2883">.png.png</code>, aí você troca no código também.</p>
<p data-start="2918" data-end="3018">Se quiser, me manda print da lista de arquivos do GitHub e eu te falo exatamente qual extensão usar.</p>
