x-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="136">Perfeito, agora deu pra ver <strong data-start="28" data-end="42">exatamente</strong> o problema 👌<br data-start="56" data-end="59">
Tá tudo certo <strong data-start="73" data-end="103">menos a Isabelle Guimarães</strong>, que ficou com o círculo branco.</p>
<p data-start="138" data-end="233">👉 <strong data-start="141" data-end="152">Motivo:</strong> o nome do arquivo da imagem dela <strong data-start="186" data-end="209">não bate exatamente</strong> com o que está no HTML.</p>
<hr data-start="235" data-end="238">
<h2 data-start="240" data-end="262">✅ O erro específico</h2>
<p data-start="263" data-end="288">No HTML você está usando:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="289" data-end="357"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">img</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">src</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"avatar-isabelle.png"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">alt</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Isabelle Guimarães"</span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="359" data-end="476">Mas no seu repositório (print que você mandou antes) o arquivo está com <strong data-start="431" data-end="449">nome diferente</strong><br data-start="449" data-end="452">
Exemplo comum que vi lá:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="477" data-end="512"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">text</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-text"><span><span>avatar-isabelle.png.png
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="513" data-end="515">ou</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="516" data-end="549"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">text</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-text"><span><span>avatar-isabel.png.png
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="551" data-end="646">➡️ Quando o nome não é <strong data-start="574" data-end="586">idêntico</strong>, o navegador não acha a imagem e mostra esse círculo vazio.</p>
<hr data-start="648" data-end="651">
<h2 data-start="653" data-end="695">✅ Duas formas de corrigir (escolhe UMA)</h2>
<h3 data-start="697" data-end="744">🔹 OPÇÃO 1 — Corrigir no HTML (mais rápido)</h3>
<p data-start="745" data-end="832">Veja o <strong data-start="752" data-end="766">nome exato</strong> do arquivo no GitHub<br data-start="787" data-end="790">
(exatamente como aparece, letra por letra)</p>
<p data-start="834" data-end="861">E altere <strong data-start="843" data-end="860">só essa linha</strong>:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="863" data-end="937"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">img</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">src</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"NOME_EXATO_DO_ARQUIVO.png"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">alt</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Isabelle Guimarães"</span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="939" data-end="968">📌 Exemplo, se o arquivo for:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="969" data-end="1004"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">text</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-text"><span><span>avatar-isabelle.png.png
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1006" data-end="1017">Então fica:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1018" data-end="1090"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">img</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">src</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"avatar-isabelle.png.png"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">alt</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Isabelle Guimarães"</span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1092" data-end="1095">
<h3 data-start="1097" data-end="1160">🔹 OPÇÃO 2 — Corrigir o nome do arquivo (mais organizado ⭐)</h3>
<p data-start="1161" data-end="1171">No GitHub:</p>
<ol data-start="1172" data-end="1251">
<li data-start="1172" data-end="1206">
