1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="96">Respira 😮‍💨 que isso é <strong data-start="25" data-end="40">bem simples</strong> e é normal acontecer quando a gente mexe muito no HTML.</p>
<p data-start="98" data-end="253">Pelo print, <strong data-start="110" data-end="139">os profissionais estão lá</strong>, mas o <strong data-start="147" data-end="203">título “Profissionais” e o texto sumiram visualmente</strong>.<br data-start="204" data-end="207">
Isso NÃO é erro de conteúdo, é <strong data-start="238" data-end="252">layout/CSS</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="255" data-end="258">
<h2 data-start="260" data-end="294">🎯 O que aconteceu (bem direto)</h2>
<p data-start="295" data-end="397">O fundo da seção e a cor do texto ficaram <strong data-start="337" data-end="353">quase iguais</strong>, então o título está lá, mas <strong data-start="383" data-end="396">invisível</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="399" data-end="511">Além disso, como o grid está com <code data-start="432" data-end="448">repeat(5, 1fr)</code> e agora tem 6 itens, o layout ficou estranho em telas grandes.</p>
<hr data-start="513" data-end="516">
<h2 data-start="518" data-end="568">✅ SOLUÇÃO RÁPIDA (2 ajustes, só copiar e colar)</h2>
<h3 data-start="570" data-end="623">🔹 1️⃣ Forçar o título “Profissionais” a aparecer</h3>
<p data-start="624" data-end="651">Procure no HTML esta parte:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="653" data-end="852"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"title"</span></span><span>&gt;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">h2</span></span></span><span>&gt;Profissionais</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">h2</span></span></span><span>&gt;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">p</span></span></span><span>&gt;</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">strong</span></span></span><span>&gt;Especialistas em Medicina Felina</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">strong</span></span></span><span>&gt;</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">br</span></span></span><span>&gt;Conheça profissionais e projetos parceiros.</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">p</span></span></span><span>&gt;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"divider"</span></span><span>&gt;</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">div</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">div</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="854" data-end="921">👉 <strong data-start="857" data-end="875">Não apaga nada</strong>, só garanta que ela esteja <strong data-start="903" data-end="917">logo acima</strong> de:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="923" data-end="953"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"pros"</span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="955" data-end="1006">Se já estiver, então o problema é só CSS (passo 2).</p>
<hr data-start="1008" data-end="1011">
<h3 data-start="1013" data-end="1049">🔹 2️⃣ Ajuste de CSS (ESSENCIAL)</h3>
<p data-start="1050" data-end="1084">No seu <code data-start="1057" data-end="1066">&lt;style&gt;</code>, <strong data-start="1068" data-end="1083">procure por</strong>:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1086" data-end="1192"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">css</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-css"><span><span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.title</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-selector-tag">h2</span></span><span>{</span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">margin</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>;</span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">font-size</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">2.25rem</span></span><span>;</span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">color</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">#3a3a3a</span></span><span>}
</span><span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.title</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-selector-tag">p</span></span><span>{</span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">margin</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">8px</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>;</span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">color</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">var</span></span><span>(--muted)}
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1194" data-end="1234">👉 <strong data-start="1197" data-end="1234">Troque por isso (copiar e colar):</strong></p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1236" data-end="1357"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">css</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-css"><span><span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.title</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-selector-tag">h2</span></span><span>{
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">margin</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">font-size</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">2.25rem</span></span><span>;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">color</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">#2b2b2b</span></span><span>;
}

</span><span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.title</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-selector-tag">p</span></span><span>{
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">margin</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">8px</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">color</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">#6f6f6f</span></span><span>;
}
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1359" data-end="1411">Isso garante contraste TOTAL com o fundo rosa claro.</p>
<hr data-start="1413" data-end="1416">
<h2 data-start="1418" data-end="1473">🎨 EXTRA (deixa ainda mais bonito – recomendo muito)</h2>
<p data-start="1474" data-end="1545">Troque o grid dos profissionais para ficar <strong data-start="1517" data-end="1544">centralizado e elegante</strong>:</p>
<h3 data-start="1547" data-end="1561">Substitua:</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1562" data-end="1679"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">css</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-css"><span><span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.pros</span></span><span>{
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">display</span></span><span>:grid;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">grid-template-columns</span></span><span>: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">repeat</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">5</span></span><span>, </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">minmax</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>,</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>fr));
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">gap</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">18px</span></span><span>;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">margin-top</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">22px</span></span><span>;
}
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="1681" data-end="1689">Por:</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1690" data-end="1843"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">css</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-css"><span><span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.pros</span></span><span>{
