<p data-start="1845" data-end="1853">👉 Isso:</p>
<ul data-start="1854" data-end="1962">
<li data-start="1854" data-end="1871">
<p data-start="1856" data-end="1871">Centraliza tudo</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1872" data-end="1913">
<p data-start="1874" data-end="1913">Funciona perfeito em notebook e celular</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1914" data-end="1962">
<p data-start="1916" data-end="1962">Dá cara de <strong data-start="1927" data-end="1962">site institucional profissional</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1964" data-end="1967">
<h2 data-start="1969" data-end="1995">✅ Resumo (bem objetivo)</h2>
<p data-start="1996" data-end="2132">✔️ Nada foi perdido<br data-start="2015" data-end="2018">
