<hr data-start="188" data-end="191">
<h2 data-start="193" data-end="227">🔴 O PROBLEMA REAL (importante)</h2>
<p data-start="228" data-end="263">O PDF <strong data-start="234" data-end="262">não está válido como PDF</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="265" data-end="292">No seu repositório aparece:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="293" data-end="325"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1"></div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>cartilha-catfriendly.pdf
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="327" data-end="381">Mas antes (e isso é o ponto-chave), você chegou a ter:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="382" data-end="418"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1"></div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>cartilha-catfriendly.pdf.png
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="420" data-end="572">Isso indica que <strong data-start="436" data-end="482">o arquivo foi convertido ou enviado errado</strong>, e o GitHub está tentando abrir <strong data-start="515" data-end="571">um arquivo corrompido ou que não é um PDF de verdade</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="574" data-end="605">👉 Por isso o navegador mostra:</p>
<blockquote data-start="606" data-end="643">
<p data-start="608" data-end="643"><strong data-start="608" data-end="643">Falha ao carregar documento PDF</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="645" data-end="648">
<h2 data-start="650" data-end="700">✅ COMO RESOLVER DEFINITIVAMENTE (passo a passo)</h2>
<h3 data-start="702" data-end="746">🔹 1️⃣ Apague o PDF atual do repositório</h3>
<p data-start="747" data-end="757">No GitHub:</p>
<ul data-start="758" data-end="838">
<li data-start="758" data-end="796">
<p data-start="760" data-end="796">Clique em <code data-start="770" data-end="796">cartilha-catfriendly.pdf</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="797" data-end="829">
<p data-start="799" data-end="829">Clique em <strong data-start="809" data-end="829">Delete this file</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="830" data-end="838">
<p data-start="832" data-end="838">Commit</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="840" data-end="843">
<h3 data-start="845" data-end="886">🔹 2️⃣ Envie o PDF ORIGINAL novamente</h3>
<p data-start="887" data-end="904">Muito importante:</p>
<p data-start="906" data-end="1059">✔️ O arquivo <strong data-start="919" data-end="950">tem que ser .pdf de verdade</strong>, não imagem<br data-start="962" data-end="965">
✔️ Não pode passar por Canva exportado como imagem<br data-start="1015" data-end="1018">
✔️ Nome exato (recomendo copiar e colar):</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1061" data-end="1093"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1"></div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>cartilha-catfriendly.pdf
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1095" data-end="1186">📌 Faça upload direto do <strong data-start="1120" data-end="1149">arquivo final da cartilha</strong> (o que você abriria no Adobe/Drive).</p>
<hr data-start="1188" data-end="1191">
<h3 data-start="1193" data-end="1228">🔹 3️⃣ Confirme antes de testar</h3>
<p data-start="1229" data-end="1246">Depois do upload:</p>
<ol data-start="1248" data-end="1366">
<li data-start="1248" data-end="1307">
<p data-start="1251" data-end="1307">Clique no arquivo <code data-start="1269" data-end="1295">cartilha-catfriendly.pdf</code> no GitHub</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1308" data-end="1366">
<p data-start="1311" data-end="1366">Ele <strong data-start="1315" data-end="1366">precisa abrir o preview do PDF dentro do GitHub</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1368" data-end="1415">👉 Se <strong data-start="1374" data-end="1391">não abrir ali</strong>, não vai abrir no site.</p>
<hr data-start="1417" data-end="1420">
<h3 data-start="1422" data-end="1469">🔹 4️⃣ Não mexa no HTML (ele já está certo)</h3>
<p data-start="1470" data-end="1499">Seu botão está correto assim:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1500" data-end="1620"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"mini-btn"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">href</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"./cartilha-catfriendly.pdf"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">target</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"_blank"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">rel</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"noopener"</span></span><span>&gt;
  Baixar Cartilha
</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1622" data-end="1660">✅ <strong data-start="1624" data-end="1660">NÃO precisa mudar nada no código</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1662" data-end="1665">
<h2 data-start="1667" data-end="1692">🧪 Teste final correto</h2>
<p data-start="1693" data-end="1710">Depois do commit:</p>
<ul data-start="1711" data-end="1787">
<li data-start="1711" data-end="1733">
<p data-start="1713" data-end="1733">Aguarde <strong data-start="1721" data-end="1733">1 minuto</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1734" data-end="1769">
<p data-start="1736" data-end="1769">Atualize o site com <strong data-start="1756" data-end="1769">Ctrl + F5</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1770" data-end="1787">
<p data-start="1772" data-end="1787">Clique no botão</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1789" data-end="1810">👉 O PDF abre normal.</p>
<hr data-start="1812" data-end="1815">
<h2 data-start="1817" data-end="1836">🧠 Resumo rápido</h2>
<p data-start="1837" data-end="1896">✔️ HTML certo<br data-start="1850" data-end="1853">
✔️ Caminho certo<br data-start="1869" data-end="1872">
❌ Arquivo PDF inválido</p>
<p data-start="1898" data-end="1929">Troca o arquivo → resolve tudo.</p>
<hr data-start="1931" data-end="1934">
<p data-start="1936" data-end="1967">Se quiser, no próximo passo eu:</p>
<ul data-start="1968" data-end="2094">
<li data-start="1968" data-end="2003">
<p data-start="1970" data-end="2003">verifico o <strong data-start="1981" data-end="2003">PDF antes de subir</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2004" data-end="2047">
<p data-start="2006" data-end="2047">te digo como exportar <strong data-start="2028" data-end="2047">100% compatível</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2048" data-end="2094">
<p data-start="2050" data-end="2094">ou faço o botão <strong data-start="2066" data-end="2094">baixar direto (download)</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2096" data-end="2192" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Você está MUITO perto do site final do PROEX — isso aqui já é detalhe técnico de acabamento 💗🐱</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copiar" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resposta satisfatória" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" a