-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="d7adaef9-9a99-48f7-a851-ba49c45d5603" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2-thinking"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="99">Entendi total pelo print — e dá pra arrumar <strong data-start="44" data-end="66">sem refazer o site</strong>. São <strong data-start="72" data-end="98">2 problemas diferentes</strong>:</p>
<ol data-start="101" data-end="237">
<li data-start="101" data-end="149">
<p data-start="104" data-end="149"><strong data-start="104" data-end="120">PDF não abre</strong> (erro do arquivo/servidor)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="150" data-end="237">
<p data-start="153" data-end="237"><strong data-start="153" data-end="177">Estrutura “quebrada”</strong> (um card ficou sem botão/estilo e o grid ficou desalinhado)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="239" data-end="294">Vou te dizer <strong data-start="252" data-end="278">exatamente o que mudar</strong>, sem enrolação.</p>
<hr data-start="296" data-end="299">
<h2 data-start="301" data-end="349">1) PDF não funciona (o jeito que NUNCA falha)</h2>
<p data-start="350" data-end="522">Mesmo quando o PDF é válido, o navegador às vezes dá “Falha ao carregar documento PDF”.<br data-start="437" data-end="440">
A solução mais estável é: <strong data-start="466" data-end="485">forçar download</strong> em vez de tentar abrir no navegador.</p>
<h3 data-start="524" data-end="570">✅ Troque o link do botão da cartilha para:</h3>
<p data-start="571" data-end="634">Procure no seu <code data-start="586" data-end="598">index.html</code> onde está a cartilha e deixe assim:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="636" data-end="734"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"mini-btn"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">href</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"./cartilha-catfriendly.pdf"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">download</span></span><span>&gt;
  Baixar Cartilha
</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="736" data-end="820">👉 O <code data-start="741" data-end="751">download</code> faz o arquivo baixar direto (não depende do visualizador do Chrome).</p>
<h3 data-start="822" data-end="875">✅ E no card da Cartilha (o primeiro card grande):</h3>
<p data-start="876" data-end="924">Procure essa linha (igual aparece no seu print):</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="925" data-end="1039"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"mini-btn"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">href</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"cartilha-catfriendly.pdf"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">target</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"_blank"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">rel</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"noopener"</span></span><span>&gt;Baixar Cartilha</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1041" data-end="1052">Troque por:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1053" data-end="1147"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"mini-btn"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">href</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"./cartilha-catfriendly.pdf"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">download</span></span><span>&gt;Baixar Cartilha</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1149" data-end="1222">Pronto. Isso resolve <strong data-start="1170" data-end="1221">mesmo que o Chrome não consiga renderizar o PDF</strong>.</p>
<blockquote data-start="1224" data-end="1363">
<p data-start="1226" data-end="1363">Se ainda assim não baixar, aí o arquivo no GitHub está corrompido — mas pelo seu print, o problema parece ser o visualizador, não o link.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="1365" data-end="1368">
<h2 data-start="1370" data-end="1448">2) Estrutura ficou estranha (card da Cartilha sem botão e grid desalinhado)</h2>
<p data-start="1449" data-end="1662">No seu print, o card “Cartilha CatFriendly” ficou com <strong data-start="1503" data-end="1535">um botão pequenininho/bugado</strong> e os cards não estão em linha. Isso é típico de HTML quebrado (tag não fechada) ou de grid com 3 colunas em tela que não cabe.</p>
<h3 data-start="1664" data-end="1720">✅ Ajuste rápido no CSS do grid (deixa sempre bonito)</h3>
<p data-start="1721" data-end="1742">No seu CSS, encontre:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1744" data-end="1850"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">css</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-css"><span><span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.feature-grid</span></span><span>{
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">display</span></span><span>:grid;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">grid-template-columns</span></span><span>: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">repeat</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">3</span></span><span>, </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">minmax</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>,</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>fr));
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">gap</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">22px</span></span><span>;
}
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1852" data-end="1863">Troque por:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1865" data-end="2007"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">css</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-css"><span><span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.feature-grid</span></span><span>{
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">display</span></span><span>:grid;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">grid-template-columns</span></span><span>: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">repeat</span></span><span>(auto-fit, </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">minmax</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">260px</span></span><span>, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>fr));
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">gap</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">22px</span></span><span>;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">align-items</span></span><span>: stretch;
}
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2009" data-end="2101">Isso faz os cards se organizarem automaticamente (sem ficar “quebrado” em telas diferentes).</p>
<hr data-start="2103" data-end="2106">
<h2 data-start="2108" data-end="2160">Me diz só 1 coisa pra eu te dar o ajuste perfeito</h2>
<p data-start="2161" data-end="2211">📌 No seu repositório, o arquivo chama exatamente:</p>
<p data-start="2213" data-end="2288"><code data-start="2213" data-end="2239">cartilha-catfriendly.pdf</code><br data-start="2239" data-end="2242">
ou está como <code data-start="2255" data-end="2265">.pdf.png</code> / <code data-start="2268" data-end="2274">.pdf</code> mas com erro?</p>
<p data-start="2290" data-end="2490">Se puder, manda <strong data-start="2306" data-end="2346">print da lista de arquivos do GitHub</strong> (tipo aquele que você mandou antes).<br data-start="2383" data-end="2386">
Aí eu confirmo em 10 segundos se o problema é arquivo ou só o visualizador — e te digo a correção exata.</p>
</div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copiar" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resposta satisfatória" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resposta insatisfatória" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-