<hr data-start="443" data-end="446">
<h2 data-start="448" data-end="470">PASSO 1 — CONFIRMAR</h2>
<p data-start="471" data-end="522">Onde você comprou o domínio <strong data-start="499" data-end="521">catfriendlylamf.io</strong>?</p>
<p data-start="524" data-end="565">Responda mentalmente (ou me diga depois):</p>
<ul data-start="566" data-end="611">
<li data-start="566" data-end="578">
<p data-start="568" data-end="578">Namecheap?</p>
</li>
<li data-start="579" data-end="589">
<p data-start="581" data-end="589">GoDaddy?</p>
</li>
<li data-start="590" data-end="602">
<p data-start="592" data-end="602">Hostinger?</p>
</li>
<li data-start="603" data-end="611">
<p data-start="605" data-end="611">Outro?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="613" data-end="664">👉 <strong data-start="616" data-end="648">É lá que a correção acontece</strong>, não no GitHub.</p>
<hr data-start="666" data-end="669">
<h2 data-start="671" data-end="723">PASSO 2 — CONFIGURAÇÃO CORRETA DE DNS (ESSENCIAL)</h2>
<p data-start="725" data-end="808">No painel do seu domínio (DNS / Zone Editor), você precisa ter <strong data-start="788" data-end="807">EXATAMENTE ISSO</strong>:</p>
<h3 data-start="810" data-end="855">🔹 APAGUE tudo que existir relacionado a:</h3>
<ul data-start="856" data-end="906">
<li data-start="856" data-end="867">
<p data-start="858" data-end="867">A antigos</p>
</li>
<li data-start="868" data-end="883">
<p data-start="870" data-end="883">CNAME errados</p>
</li>
<li data-start="884" data-end="906">
<p data-start="886" data-end="906">Registros duplicados</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="908" data-end="933">Depois, crie <strong data-start="921" data-end="932">do zero</strong>:</p>
<hr data-start="935" data-end="938">
<h3 data-start="940" data-end="972">✅ REGISTROS A (obrigatórios)</h3>
<p data-start="974" data-end="1003">Crie <strong data-start="979" data-end="996">4 registros A</strong> assim:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1005" data-end="1067"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">makefile</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span><span class="hljs-section">Tipo: A</span></span><span>
