<p data-start="1261" data-end="1318">⚠️ <strong data-start="1264" data-end="1280">O Host é <code data-start="1275" data-end="1278">@</code></strong>, não coloca <code data-start="1293" data-end="1313">catfriendlylamf.io</code> ali.</p>
<hr data-start="1320" data-end="1323">
<h3 data-start="1325" data-end="1372">✅ REGISTRO CNAME (opcional mas recomendado)</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1374" data-end="1455"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">makefile</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span><span class="hljs-section">Tipo: CNAME</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-section">Host: www</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-section">Valor: leandralima906-hue.github.io</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-section">TTL: automático</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1457" data-end="1460">
<h2 data-start="1462" data-end="1491">PASSO 3 — VOLTAR AO GITHUB</h2>
<p data-start="1492" data-end="1515">Depois de salvar o DNS:</p>
<ol data-start="1517" data-end="1721">
<li data-start="1517" data-end="1563">
<p data-start="1520" data-end="1563">Volte em<br data-start="1528" data-end="1531">
<strong data-start="1534" data-end="1563">GitHub → Settings → Pages</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1564" data-end="1631">
<p data-start="1567" data-end="1595">Em <strong data-start="1570" data-end="1587">Custom domain</strong>, deixe:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1599" data-end="1631"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">lua</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>catfriendlylamf.</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">io</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
</li>
<li data-start="1632" data-end="1653">
<p data-start="1635" data-end="1653">Clique em <strong data-start="1645" data-end="1653">Save</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1654" data-end="1682">
<p data-start="1657" data-end="1682">Espere <strong data-start="1664" data-end="1682">5 a 30 minutos</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1683" data-end="1721">
<p data-start="1686" data-end="1721">Clique em <strong data-start="1696" data-end="1721">“Verifique novamente”</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1723" data-end="1785">⚠️ Às vezes pode levar até <strong data-start="1750" data-end="1760">1 hora</strong> (DNS não é instantâneo).</p>
<hr data-start="1787" data-end="1790">
<h2 data-start="1792" data-end="1826">PASSO 4 — HTTPS (cadeadinho 🔒)</h2>
<p data-start="1827" data-end="1854">Quando o DNS estiver certo:</p>
<ul data-start="1855" data-end="1948">
<li data-start="1855" data-end="1877">
<p data-start="1857" data-end="1877">O erro vermelho some</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1878" data-end="1912">
<p data-start="1880" data-end="1912">A opção <strong data-start="1888" data-end="1905">“Impor HTTPS”</strong> libera</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1913" data-end="1936">
<p data-start="1915" data-end="1936">Você marca a caixinha</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1937" data-end="1948">
<p data-start="1939" data-end="1948">Pronto ✔️</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1950" data-end="1953">
<h2 data-start="1955" data-end="2013">IMPORTANTE (erro comum que você NÃO cometeu, mas aviso)</h2>
<p data-start="2014" data-end="2102">❌ Não é erro do PDF<br data-start="2033" data-end="2036">
❌ Não é erro do HTML<br data-start="2056" data-end="2059">
❌ Não é erro do botão<br data-start="2080" data-end="2083">
✔️ É <strong data-start="2088" data-end="2102">apenas DNS</strong></p>
<p data-start="2104" data-end="2164">Quando o domínio funcionar, <strong data-start="2132" data-end="2163">o PDF vai abrir normalmente</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="2166" data-end="2169">
<h2 data-start="2171" data-end="2203">QUER QUE EU CONFIRA COM VOCÊ?</h2>
<p data-start="2204" data-end="2230">Se você quiser, faz assim:</p>
<ul data-start="2231" data-end="2310">
<li data-start="2231" data-end="2267">
<p data-start="2233" data-end="2267">Me diga <strong data-start="2241" data-end="2267">onde comprou o domínio</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2268" data-end="2310">
<p data-start="2270" data-end="2310">Me diga <strong data-start="2278" data-end="2310">o que aparece na tela de DNS</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2312" data-end="2376">Eu te digo:<br>
👉 “apaga esse”<br>
👉 “corrige esse”<br>
👉 “esse tá certo”</p>
<p data-start="2378" data-end="2459" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Você tá fazendo algo que MUITA gente trava — e você chegou longe pra caramba 🐱💗</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copiar" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resposta satisfatória" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resp