<hr data-start="173" data-end="176">
<h1 data-start="178" data-end="208">🔴 PARTE 1 — DNS (DOMÍNIO)</h1>
<p data-start="209" data-end="295">👉 <strong data-start="212" data-end="237">Isso é fora do GitHub</strong>, no site onde você comprou o domínio <code data-start="275" data-end="295">catfriendlylamf.io</code></p>
<h2 data-start="297" data-end="315">1️⃣ APAGUE TUDO</h2>
<p data-start="316" data-end="393">No painel de <strong data-start="329" data-end="350">DNS / Zone Editor</strong>, <strong data-start="352" data-end="381">DELETE TODOS OS REGISTROS</strong> existentes:</p>
<ul data-start="394" data-end="443">
<li data-start="394" data-end="399">
<p data-start="396" data-end="399">A</p>
</li>
<li data-start="400" data-end="409">
<p data-start="402" data-end="409">CNAME</p>
</li>
<li data-start="410" data-end="418">
<p data-start="412" data-end="418">AAAA</p>
</li>
<li data-start="419" data-end="426">
<p data-start="421" data-end="426">TXT</p>
</li>
<li data-start="427" data-end="443">
<p data-start="429" data-end="443">Qualquer coisa</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="445" data-end="470">Deixa <strong data-start="451" data-end="469">ZERO registros</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="472" data-end="475">
