<hr data-start="1054" data-end="1057">
<h1 data-start="1059" data-end="1096">🟢 PARTE 2 — GITHUB PAGES (DOMÍNIO)</h1>
<p data-start="1098" data-end="1112">Depois do DNS:</p>
<ol data-start="1114" data-end="1368">
<li data-start="1114" data-end="1170">
<p data-start="1117" data-end="1170">Vá em<br data-start="1122" data-end="1125">
<strong data-start="1128" data-end="1170">GitHub → Repository → Settings → Pages</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1171" data-end="1240">
<p data-start="1174" data-end="1204">Em <strong data-start="1177" data-end="1194">Custom domain</strong>, escreva:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1208" data-end="1240"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">lua</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>catfriendlylamf.</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">io</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
</li>
<li data-start="1241" data-end="1262">
<p data-start="1244" data-end="1262">Clique em <strong data-start="1254" data-end="1262">Save</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1263" data-end="1291">
<p data-start="1266" data-end="1291">Aguarde <strong data-start="1274" data-end="1291">10–30 minutos</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1292" data-end="1321">
<p data-start="1295" data-end="1321">Clique em <strong data-start="1305" data-end="1321">Verify again</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1322" data-end="1368">
<p data-start="1325" data-end="1368">Quando liberar → marque <strong data-start="1349" data-end="1368">“Enforce HTTPS”</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1370" data-end="1420">⚠️ Se não liberar na hora: <strong data-start="1397" data-end="1407">normal</strong>, DNS demora.</p>
<hr data-start="1422" data-end="1425">
<h1 data-start="1427" data-end="1467">🔵 PARTE 3 — PDF NÃO ABRIA (AGORA VAI)</h1>
<h2 data-start="1469" data-end="1490">ERRO QUE VOCÊ TEVE</h2>
<p data-start="1491" data-end="1553">O arquivo <strong data-start="1501" data-end="1512">existia</strong>, mas o GitHub não conseguia ler direito.</p>
<p data-start="1555" data-end="1580">👉 <strong data-start="1558" data-end="1577">Solução correta</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="1581" data-end="1646">
<li data-start="1581" data-end="1614">
<p data-start="1583" data-end="1614">O PDF precisa estar <strong data-start="1603" data-end="1614">na raiz</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1615" data-end="1646">
<p data-start="1617" data-end="1646">O nome precisa bater <strong data-start="1638" data-end="1646">100%</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1648" data-end="1651">
