<hr data-start="1304" data-end="1307">
<h2 data-start="1309" data-end="1338">💥 Por que não funcionava?</h2>
<p data-start="1339" data-end="1371">Porque o navegador estava lendo:</p>
<ul data-start="1372" data-end="1424">
<li data-start="1372" data-end="1396">
<p data-start="1374" data-end="1396">um <code data-start="1377" data-end="1382">&lt;a&gt;</code> <strong data-start="1383" data-end="1396">sem texto</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1397" data-end="1424">
<p data-start="1399" data-end="1424"><strong data-start="1399" data-end="1424">sem fechamento <code data-start="1416" data-end="1422">&lt;/a&gt;</code></strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1426" data-end="1496">Isso quebra o HTML <strong data-start="1445" data-end="1478">e bagunça tudo que vem depois</strong> (layout + links).</p>
<hr data-start="1498" data-end="1501">
<h2 data-start="1503" data-end="1521">✔️ Depois disso</h2>
