n-w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="a6cc1e0a-009d-46e2-9b84-483008b79c80" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="143">Respira 💗 isso <strong data-start="16" data-end="52">não é erro do site nem do código</strong>. É <strong data-start="56" data-end="68">100% DNS</strong> — e é normal quando o domínio ainda <strong data-start="105" data-end="142">não foi configurado ou não existe</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="145" data-end="188">Vou explicar <strong data-start="158" data-end="172">bem direto</strong>, sem te afogar.</p>
<hr data-start="190" data-end="193">
<h2 data-start="195" data-end="225">❌ O que significa esse erro</h2>
<blockquote data-start="226" data-end="259">
<p data-start="228" data-end="259"><strong data-start="228" data-end="259">DNS_PROBE_FINISHED_NXDOMAIN</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="261" data-end="394">Quer dizer:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="276" data-end="338">o domínio `catfriendlylamf.io NÃO existe na internet ainda</strong><br data-start="338" data-end="341">
ou<br data-start="343" data-end="346">
👉 existe, mas <strong data-start="361" data-end="393">não aponta para lugar nenhum</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="396" data-end="445">O GitHub <strong data-start="405" data-end="425">não cria domínio</strong>. Ele só <strong data-start="434" data-end="444">recebe</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="447" data-end="450">
<h2 data-start="452" data-end="511">✅ Pra ter <code data-start="465" data-end="485">catfriendlylamf.io</code>, você precisa de 2 coisas</h2>
<h3 data-start="513" data-end="538">1️⃣ COMPRAR o domínio</h3>
<p data-start="539" data-end="568">Você já comprou esse domínio?</p>
<p data-start="570" data-end="595">Exemplos de onde comprar:</p>
<ul data-start="596" data-end="652">
<li data-start="596" data-end="611">
<p data-start="598" data-end="611">Registro.br</p>
</li>
<li data-start="612" data-end="625">
<p data-start="614" data-end="625">Hostinger</p>
</li>
<li data-start="626" data-end="637">
<p data-start="628" data-end="637">GoDaddy</p>
</li>
<li data-start="638" data-end="652">
<p data-start="640" data-end="652">Cloudflare</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="654" data-end="717">⚠️ Se <strong data-start="660" data-end="675">não comprou</strong>, ele <strong data-start="681" data-end="700">nunca vai abrir</strong>, mesmo perfeito.</p>
<p data-start="719" data-end="762">👉 Se <strong data-start="725" data-end="740">não comprou</strong>, pare aqui e me diga:</p>
<blockquote data-start="763" data-end="788">
<p data-start="765" data-end="788"><strong data-start="765" data-end="788">“Não comprei ainda”</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="790" data-end="793">
<h3 data-start="795" data-end="833">2️⃣ CONFIGURAR O DNS (obrigatório)</h3>
<p data-start="834" data-end="908">Depois de comprar, você precisa <strong data-start="866" data-end="907">apontar o domínio para o GitHub Pages</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="910" data-end="961">Os registros são esses 👇<br data-start="935" data-end="938">
(iguais pra todo mundo)</p>
<h4 data-start="963" data-end="982">🔹 Registros A</h4>
<p data-start="983" data-end="1032">No painel do domínio, adicione <strong data-start="1014" data-end="1031">4 registros A</strong>:</p>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="1034" data-end="1186" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="1034" data-end="1057"><tr data-start="1034" data-end="1057"><th data-start="1034" data-end="1041" data-col-size="sm">Tipo</th><th data-start="1041" data-end="1048" data-col-size="sm">Nome</th><th data-start="1048" data-end="1057" data-col-size="sm">Valor</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="1075" data-end="1186"><tr data-start="1075" data-end="1102"><td data-start="1075" data-end="1079" data-col-size="sm">A</td><td data-start="1079" data-end="1083" data-col-size="sm">@</td><td data-start="1083" data-end="1102" data-col-size="sm">185.199.108.153</td></tr><tr data-start="1103" data-end="1130"><td data-start="1103" data-end="1107" data-col-size="sm">A</td><td data-start="1107" data-end="1111" data-col-size="sm">@</td><td data-start="1111" data-end="1130" data-col-size="sm">185.199.109.153</td></tr><tr data-start="1131" data-end="1158"><td data-start="1131" data-end="1135" data-col-size="sm">A</td><td data-start="1135" data-end="1139" data-col-size="sm">@</td><td data-start="1139" data-end="1158" data-col-size="sm">185.199.110.153</td></tr><tr data-start="1159" data-end="1186"><td data-start="1159" data-end="1163" data-col-size="sm">A</td><td data-start="1163" data-end="1167" data-col-size="sm">@</td><td data-start="1167" data-end="1186" data-col-size="sm">185.199.111.153</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 32.6562px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copiar tabela" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<h4 data-start="1188" data-end="1210">🔹 Registro CNAME</h4>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="1211" data-end="1298" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="1211" data-end="1234"><tr data-start="1211" data-end="1234"><th data-start="1211" data-end="1218" data-col-size="sm">Tipo</th><th data-start="1218" data-end="1225" data-col-size="sm">Nome</th><th data-start="1225" data-end="1234" data-col-size="sm">Valor</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="1252" data-end="1298"><tr data-start="1252" data-end="1298"><td data-start="1252" data-end="1260" data-col-size="sm">CNAME</td><td data-start="1260" data-end="1266" data-col-size="sm">www</td><td data-start="1266" data-end="1298" data-col-size="sm">leandralima906-hue.github.io</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 32.6562px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copiar tabela" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<hr data-start="1300" data-end="1303">
<h3 data-start="1305" data-end="1335">3️⃣ Depois VOLTA no GitHub</h3>
<p data-start="1336" data-end="1339">Em:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1340" data-end="1362">
<p data-start="1342" data-end="1362"><strong data-start="1342" data-end="1362">Settings → Pages</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="1364" data-end="1371">Coloca:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1372" data-end="1398"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">lua</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>catfriendlylamf.</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">io</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1400" data-end="1460">✔️ Marca <strong data-start="1409" data-end="1426">Enforce HTTPS</strong> (só aparece depois que funcionar)</p>
<p data-start="1462" data-end="1524">⏳ Pode demorar <strong data-start="1477" data-end="1491">até 1 hora</strong> (às vezes 10 min, às vezes 24h).</p>
<hr data-start="1526" data-end="1529">
<h2 data-start="1531" data-end="1564">🚨 Importante (pra não surtar)</h2>
<ul data-start="1565" data-end="1640">
<li data-start="1565" data-end="1600">
<p data-start="1567" data-end="1600">Esse erro <strong data-start="1577" data-end="1600">não quebra seu site</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1601" data-end="1640">
<p data-start="1603" data-end="1640">Seu site <strong data-start="1612" data-end="1636">continua funcionando</strong> em:</p>
</li>
</ul>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1641" data-end="1703"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">bash</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>https://leandralima906-hue.github.io/catfriendly-site/
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<ul data-start="1704" data-end="1737">
<li data-start="1704" data-end="1737">
<p data-start="1706" data-end="1737">O domínio só é “apelido bonito”</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1739" data-end="1742">
