 [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="87">Perfeito, isso é <strong data-start="17" data-end="32">bem simples</strong> 💗<br data-start="35" data-end="38">
Vou te explicar <strong data-start="54" data-end="71">passo a passo</strong>, sem enrolação.</p>
<hr data-start="89" data-end="92">
<h2 data-start="94" data-end="135">✅ COMO TIRAR O DOMÍNIO DO GITHUB PAGES</h2>
<h3 data-start="137" data-end="173">1️⃣ Entre no repositório do site</h3>
<p data-start="174" data-end="198">👉 aquele do CatFriendly</p>
<hr data-start="200" data-end="203">
<h3 data-start="205" data-end="219">2️⃣ Vá em:</h3>
<p data-start="220" data-end="240"><strong data-start="220" data-end="240">Settings → Pages</strong></p>
<hr data-start="242" data-end="245">
<h3 data-start="247" data-end="281">3️⃣ Na parte <strong data-start="264" data-end="281">Custom domain</strong></h3>
<p data-start="282" data-end="295">Você vai ver:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="296" data-end="322"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">lua</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>catfriendlylamf.</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">io</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="324" data-end="370">👉 <strong data-start="327" data-end="347">APAGA esse texto</strong><br data-start="347" data-end="350">
👉 Clica em <strong data-start="362" data-end="370">Save</strong></p>
<p data-start="372" data-end="402">⚠️ Não deixa nada escrito ali.</p>
<hr data-start="404" data-end="407">
<h3 data-start="409" data-end="426">4️⃣ Pronto 🎉</h3>
<p data-start="427" data-end="503">Agora o site volta a funcionar <strong data-start="458" data-end="473">normalmente</strong> no endereço padrão do GitHub:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="505" data-end="567"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">bash</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>https://leandralima906-hue.github.io/catfriendly-site/
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="569" data-end="572">
<h2 data-start="574" data-end="598">🔎 Se ainda não abrir</h2>
<p data-start="599" data-end="622">Faça isso (importante):</p>
<ul data-start="624" data-end="701">
<li data-start="624" data-end="676">
<p data-start="626" data-end="676">Aperta <strong data-start="633" data-end="646">Ctrl + F5</strong> (ou limpa cache do navegador)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="677" data-end="701">
<p data-start="679" data-end="701">Espera <strong data-start="686" data-end="701">1–5 minutos</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="703" data-end="706">
<h2 data-start="708" data-end="746">❗ Importante (bem importante mesmo)</h2>
<p data-start="747" data-end="775">Depois de remover o domínio:</p>
<ul data-start="776" data-end="873">
<li data-start="776" data-end="805">
<p data-start="778" data-end="805">❌ NÃO marca “Enforce HTTPS”</p>
</li>
<li data-start="806" data-end="835">
<p data-start="808" data-end="835">❌ NÃO coloca domínio nenhum</p>
</li>
<li data-start="836" data-end="873">
<p data-start="838" data-end="873">✔️ Deixa só <strong data-start="850" data-end="873">Branch: main / root</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="875" data-end="878">
<h2 data-start="880" data-end="900">💬 Depois me diz:</h2>
<ul data-start="901" data-end="1000">
<li data-start="901" data-end="934">
<p data-start="903" data-end="934">🔹 O site abriu no link padrão?</p>
</li>
<li data-start="935" data-end="1000">
<p data-start="937" data-end="1000">🔹 Quer que eu te ajude <strong data-start="961" data-end="988">a consertar o PDF agora</strong> (é rápido)?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1002" data-end="1060" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Você fez MUITA coisa certa, isso aqui é só ajuste final 💕</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copiar" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resposta satisfatória" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resposta insatisfatória" a