g"><p data-start="0" data-end="128">Respira 😮‍💨💗 deu <strong data-start="20" data-end="28">B.O.</strong>, mas <strong data-start="34" data-end="70">tá tudo explicável e consertável</strong>. Vou ser <strong data-start="80" data-end="94">bem direta</strong>, passo a passo, sem código agora.</p>
<hr data-start="130" data-end="133">
<h2 data-start="135" data-end="178">✅ SITUAÇÃO ATUAL (o que a imagem mostra)</h2>
<p data-start="179" data-end="256">Isso aqui é o MAIS IMPORTANTE 👇<br data-start="211" data-end="214">
👉 <strong data-start="217" data-end="240">Seu site ESTÁ no ar</strong> neste endereço:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="258" data-end="320"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">bash</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>https://leandralima906-hue.github.io/catfriendly-site/
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="322" data-end="423">O GitHub confirmou isso (“Your site is live at…”).<br data-start="372" data-end="375">
Então o problema <strong data-start="392" data-end="422">NÃO é o GitHub Pages em si</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="425" data-end="428">
<h2 data-start="430" data-end="490">❌ PROBLEMA 1 — Domínio personalizado (catfriendlylamf.io)</h2>
<p data-start="491" data-end="506">Esse erro aqui:</p>
<blockquote data-start="508" data-end="539">
<p data-start="510" data-end="539"><code data-start="510" data-end="539">DNS_PROBE_FINISHED_NXDOMAIN</code></p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="541" data-end="699">significa <strong data-start="551" data-end="567">uma coisa só</strong>:<br>
➡️ <strong data-start="572" data-end="618">o domínio NÃO está apontando para o GitHub</strong><br data-start="618" data-end="621">
(e isso não se resolve no GitHub, e sim no lugar onde você comprou o domínio).</p>
<h3 data-start="701" data-end="736">Como REMOVER o domínio (de vez)</h3>
<p data-start="737" data-end="773">Você já está quase lá, só faça isso:</p>
<ol data-start="775" data-end="963">
<li data-start="775" data-end="821">
<p data-start="778" data-end="821"><strong data-start="778" data-end="821">GitHub → Repositório → Settings → Pages</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="822" data-end="916">
<p data-start="825" data-end="853">Em <strong data-start="828" data-end="853">Domínio personalizado</strong></p>
<ul data-start="857" data-end="916">
<li data-start="857" data-end="890">
<p data-start="859" data-end="890">Apague tudo que estiver escrito</p>
</li>
<li data-start="894" data-end="916">
<p data-start="896" data-end="916">Clique em <strong data-start="906" data-end="916">Remove</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="917" data-end="942">
<p data-start="920" data-end="942">Espere <strong data-start="927" data-end="942">1–3 minutos</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="943" data-end="963">
<p data-start="946" data-end="963">Atualize a página</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="965" data-end="1068">⚠️ <strong data-start="968" data-end="1006">Import HTTPS não precisa desmarcar</strong><br data-start="1006" data-end="1009">
(ele fica automático quando usa <code data-start="1041" data-end="1052">github.io</code>, isso é normal)</p>
<p data-start="1070" data-end="1150">Depois disso:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="1087" data-end="1150">IGNORE totalmente o domínio catfriendlylamf.io por enquanto</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1152" data-end="1155">
<h2 data-start="1157" data-end="1206">❌ PROBLEMA 2 — PDF não abre (esse é no código)</h2>
<p data-start="1207" data-end="1261">Aqui está o erro real 👇<br data-start="1231" data-end="1234">
No seu HTML, você tem isso:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1263" data-end="1360"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"mini-btn"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">href</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"./cartilha-catfriendly.pdf"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">target</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"_blank"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">rel</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"noopener"</span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1362" data-end="1450">⚠️ <strong data-start="1365" data-end="1401">Mas o botão NÃO tem texto dentro</strong><br data-start="1401" data-end="1404">
e em outro ponto você usa caminhos diferentes.</p>
<h3 data-start="1452" data-end="1495">REGRA DO GITHUB PAGES (importantíssima)</h3>
<p data-start="1496" data-end="1518">Como seu site está em:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1520" data-end="1546"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">bash</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>/catfriendly-site/
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1548" data-end="1607">👉 <strong data-start="1551" data-end="1607">TODOS os links para arquivos precisam respeitar isso</strong></p>
<h3 data-start="1609" data-end="1657">✅ Forma CERTA (use essa em TODOS os lugares)</h3>
