<h3 data-start="73" data-end="89">❌ O problema</h3>
<p data-start="90" data-end="125">Seu <strong data-start="94" data-end="124">PDF está com o nome errado</strong>:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="127" data-end="163"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1"></div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>cartilha-catfriendly.pdf.pgn
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="165" data-end="173">Ou seja:</p>
<ul data-start="174" data-end="272">
<li data-start="174" data-end="192">
<p data-start="176" data-end="192">tem <strong data-start="180" data-end="192">.pdf.pgn</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="193" data-end="218">
<p data-start="195" data-end="218">o site procura <strong data-start="210" data-end="218">.pdf</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="219" data-end="272">
<p data-start="221" data-end="272">por isso o botão <strong data-start="238" data-end="250">não abre</strong> e o navegador dá erro</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="274" data-end="277">
<h3 data-start="279" data-end="314">✅ Como corrigir (passo a passo)</h3>
<h4 data-start="316" data-end="343">1️⃣ Renomeie o arquivo</h4>
<p data-start="344" data-end="373">No GitHub, clique no arquivo:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="375" data-end="411"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1"></div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>cartilha-catfriendly.pdf.pgn
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="413" data-end="475">→ clique em <strong data-start="425" data-end="443">Rename (lápis)</strong><br data-start="443" data-end="446">
→ troque para <strong data-start="460" data-end="474">EXATAMENTE</strong>:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="477" data-end="509"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1"></div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>cartilha-catfriendly.pdf
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="511" data-end="550">⚠️ <strong data-start="514" data-end="533">Apague o <code data-start="525" data-end="531">.pgn</code></strong>, deixe só <code data-start="544" data-end="550">.pdf</code></p>
<p data-start="552" data-end="588">Depois clique em <strong data-start="569" data-end="587">Commit changes</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="590" data-end="593">
<h3 data-start="595" data-end="638">🧹 2️⃣ Apague o arquivo errado (imagem)</h3>
