tems-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2-thinking"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="216">Entendi — e pelo seu print anterior dá pra ver exatamente por quê: <strong data-start="67" data-end="114">o “PDF” que está aí não é um PDF de verdade</strong> (é uma imagem/arquivo errado com extensão bagunçada). Renomear só o nome <strong data-start="188" data-end="204">não conserta</strong> o conteúdo.</p>
<p data-start="218" data-end="276">Vamos resolver do jeito que <strong data-start="246" data-end="263">funciona 100%</strong>, sem sofrer:</p>
<hr data-start="278" data-end="281">
<h2 data-start="283" data-end="342">✅ 1) Apague os arquivos errados da cartilha (2 arquivos)</h2>
<p data-start="343" data-end="376">No seu repositório, delete estes:</p>
<ul data-start="378" data-end="478">
<li data-start="378" data-end="428">
<p data-start="380" data-end="428"><code data-start="380" data-end="410">cartilha-catfriendly.pdf.pgn</code>  (isso NÃO é pdf)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="429" data-end="478">
<p data-start="431" data-end="478"><code data-start="431" data-end="457">cartilha-catfriendly.png</code>      (isso é imagem)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="480" data-end="494">✅ Mantenha só:</p>
<ul data-start="495" data-end="532">
<li data-start="495" data-end="532">
<p data-start="497" data-end="532"><code data-start="497" data-end="516">cartilha-capa.png</code> (essa é a capa)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="534" data-end="537">
<h2 data-start="539" data-end="597">✅ 2) Faça upload do PDF verdadeiro (o arquivo original)</h2>
<p data-start="598" data-end="689">Agora, suba o arquivo <strong data-start="620" data-end="628">real</strong> que você tem no celular/PC (o PDF que abre no seu aparelho).</p>
<h3 data-start="691" data-end="705">No GitHub:</h3>
<p data-start="706" data-end="733"><strong data-start="706" data-end="733">Add file → Upload files</strong></p>
<p data-start="735" data-end="773">E envie o PDF com este nome <strong data-start="763" data-end="772">exato</strong>:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="774" data-end="806"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1"></div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>cartilha-catfriendly.pdf
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="808" data-end="856">⚠️ Certifique que o arquivo é realmente <strong data-start="848" data-end="855">PDF</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="857" data-end="948">
<li data-start="857" data-end="910">
<p data-start="859" data-end="910">no celular normalmente aparece como “Documento PDF”</p>
</li>
<li data-start="911" data-end="948">
<p data-start="913" data-end="948">no computador ele termina em <code data-start="942" data-end="948">.pdf</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="950" data-end="953">
<h2 data-start="955" data-end="1009">✅ 3) Teste do jeito certo (antes de testar no site)</h2>
<p data-start="1010" data-end="1027">Depois do upload:</p>
<ol data-start="1029" data-end="1171">
<li data-start="1029" data-end="1095">
<p data-start="1032" data-end="1095">Clique no arquivo <code data-start="1050" data-end="1076">cartilha-catfriendly.pdf</code> dentro do GitHub</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1096" data-end="1171">
<p data-start="1099" data-end="1171">O GitHub deve mostrar o preview do PDF (ou pelo menos oferecer download)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1173" data-end="1242">Se o GitHub <strong data-start="1185" data-end="1208">não conseguir abrir</strong>, então o arquivo ainda não é PDF.</p>
<hr data-start="1244" data-end="1247">
<h2 data-start="1249" data-end="1297">✅ 4) Deixe seus links assim (os dois lugares)</h2>
<p data-start="1298" data-end="1353">No seu <code data-start="1305" data-end="1317">index.html</code>, garanta que está exatamente assim:</p>
<h3 data-start="1355" data-end="1373">Botão no card:</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1374" data-end="1514"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"mini-btn"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">href</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"./cartilha-catfriendly.pdf"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">target</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"_blank"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">rel</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"noopener noreferrer"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">download</span></span><span>&gt;
