<hr data-start="97" data-end="100">
<h2 data-start="102" data-end="138">1️⃣ Suba a imagem da logo da LAMF</h2>
<p data-start="139" data-end="213">No repositório do GitHub, coloque a logo com um nome simples, por exemplo:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="215" data-end="236"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1"></div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>logo-lamf.png
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="238" data-end="301">👉 deixe <strong data-start="247" data-end="281">na mesma pasta do <code data-start="267" data-end="279">index.html</code></strong> (igual os avatars).</p>
<hr data-start="303" data-end="306">
<h2 data-start="308" data-end="352">2️⃣ Ache ESTE trecho no seu HTML (NAVBAR)</h2>
<p data-start="353" data-end="414">Procure por isso no <code data-start="373" data-end="385">index.html</code> (bem no começo do <code data-start="404" data-end="412">&lt;body&gt;</code>):</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="416" data-end="748"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"brand"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">href</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"#inicio"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">aria-label</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Ir para o início"</span></span><span>&gt;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">span</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"brand-badge"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">aria-hidden</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"true"</span></span><span>&gt;
    </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">svg</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">width</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"20"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">height</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"20"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">viewBox</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"0 0 24 24"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">fill</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"none"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">xmlns</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"</span></span><span>&gt;
      ...
    </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">svg</span></span></span><span>&gt;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">span</span></span></span><span>&gt;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span></span></span><span>&gt;
    Projeto CatFriendly
    </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">small</span></span></span><span>&gt;LAMF • UNIFAA</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">small</span></span></span><span>&gt;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">div</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="750" data-end="753">
<h2 data-start="755" data-end="805">3️⃣ SUBSTITUA tudo isso por 👇 (copiar e colar)</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="806" data-end="1022"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"brand"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">href</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"#inicio"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">aria-label</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Ir para o início"</span></span><span>&gt;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">img</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">src</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"logo-lamf.png"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">alt</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Logo LAMF"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"logo-lamf"</span></span><span>&gt;

  </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span></span></span><span>&gt;
    Projeto CatFriendly
    </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">small</span></span></span><span>&gt;LAMF • UNIFAA</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">small</span></span></span><span>&gt;
