<h2 data-start="111" data-end="145">1️⃣ Salva a logo no repositório</h2>
<p data-start="147" data-end="207">No GitHub, salva essa imagem com <strong data-start="180" data-end="193">este nome</strong> (importante):</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="209" data-end="230"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1"></div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span>logo-lamf.png
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="232" data-end="309">👉 Coloca <strong data-start="242" data-end="276">na mesma pasta do <code data-start="262" data-end="274">index.html</code></strong> (igual você fez com os avatars).</p>
<hr data-start="311" data-end="314">
<h2 data-start="316" data-end="356">2️⃣ Onde mexer no HTML (só na NAVBAR)</h2>
<p data-start="358" data-end="415">Procura <strong data-start="366" data-end="381">ESTE trecho</strong> no seu <code data-start="389" data-end="401">index.html</code> (lá em cima):</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="417" data-end="491"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"brand"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">href</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"#inicio"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">aria-label</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Ir para o início"</span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="493" data-end="587">E <strong data-start="495" data-end="534">substitui TUDO que está dentro dele</strong> por isso aqui ⬇️<br data-start="551" data-end="554">
(só copiar e colar, pode confiar)</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="589" data-end="805"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">html</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-html"><span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"brand"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">href</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"#inicio"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">aria-label</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Ir para o início"</span></span><span>&gt;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">img</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">src</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"logo-lamf.png"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">alt</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Logo LAMF"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">class</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"logo-lamf"</span></span><span>&gt;

  </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span></span></span><span>&gt;
    Projeto CatFriendly
    </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">small</span></span></span><span>&gt;LAMF • UNIFAA</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">small</span></span></span><span>&gt;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">div</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="807" data-end="810">
<h2 data-start="812" data-end="847">3️⃣ Agora adiciona o CSS da logo</h2>
<p data-start="849" data-end="915">Dentro do <code data-start="859" data-end="868">&lt;style&gt;</code> (pode ser logo depois de <code data-start="894" data-end="902">.brand</code>), cola isso:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="917" data-end="1047"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl corner-superellipse/1.1 relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl corner-t-superellipse/1.1">css</div><div class="sticky top-[calc(--spacing(9)+var(--header-height))] @w-xl/main:top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="Copiar"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Copiar código</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-css"><span><span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.logo-lamf</span></span><span>{
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">width</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">42px</span></span><span>;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">height</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">42px</span></span><span>;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">object-fit</span></span><span>:contain;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">border-radius</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">50%</span></span><span>;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">background</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">#fff</span></span><span>;
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attribute">padding</span></span><span>:</span><span><span class="hljs-number">4px</span></span><span>;
}
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1049" data-end="1060">✨ Isso vai:</p>
<ul data-start="1061" data-end="1188">
<li data-start="1061" data-end="1091">
<p data-start="1063" data-end="1091">deixar a logo <strong data-start="1077" data-end="1091">redondinha</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1092" data-end="1138">
<p data-start="1094" data-end="1138">com fundo branco (fica linda na navbar rosa)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1139" data-end="1188">
<p data-start="1141" data-end="1188">alinhada à esquerda, do jeitinho que você pediu</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1190" data-end="1193">
<h2 data-start="1195" data-end="1239">4️⃣ Resultado final (o que vai acontecer)</h2>
<p data-start="1241" data-end="1397">✔ Logo da LAMF no <strong data-start="1259" data-end="1286">canto superior esquerdo</strong><br data-start="1286" data-end="1289">
✔ Nome “Projeto CatFriendly” ao lado<br data-start="1325" data-end="1328">
✔ Visual profissional, acadêmico e limpo<br data-start="1368" data-end="1371">
✔ Zero bagunça no layout</p>
<hr data-start="1399" data-end="1402">
<p data-start="1404" data-end="1446">Se você quiser, no próximo passo eu posso:</p>
<ul data-start="1447" data-end="1575">
<li data-start="1447" data-end="1476">
<p data-start="1449" data-end="1476">🔹 aumentar/diminuir a logo</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1477" data-end="1514">
<p data-start="1479" data-end="1514">🔹 deixar <strong data-start="1489" data-end="1502">só a logo</strong> (sem texto)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1515" data-end="1551">
<p data-start="1517" data-end="1551">🔹 colocar a logo da UNIFAA também</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1552" data-end="1575">
<p data-start="1554" data-end="1575">🔹 ajustar pra mobile</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1577" data-end="1657" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Respira 😮‍💨 — agora a parte difícil já passou e ficou <strong data-start="1633" data-end="1654">bonito de verdade</strong> 💗</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copiar" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Resposta satisfatória" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-k5zux585.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-to